\"Thu, 20 Apr 2023 16:27:26 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:4:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:4:\"Blog\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:8:\"SEO Tips\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:22:\"Google snippet preview\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:20:\"SERP snippet preview\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:28:\"https://aioseo.com/?p=177317\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:430:\"<p>Would you like to learn how to use the Google snippet preview to boost your SEO? The preview is a picture of your page in Google search results. By using a preview, you can find and fix errors before publishing.&#8230;</p>\nThe post <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-use-google-snippet-preview-to-boost-seo/\">How to Use the Google Snippet Preview to Boost Your SEO</a> first appeared on <a href=\"https://aioseo.com\">AIOSEO</a>.\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:15:\"Sherrie Gossett\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:34064:\"<p>Would you like to learn how to use the Google snippet preview to boost your SEO?</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The preview is a picture of your page in Google search results. By using a preview, you can find and fix errors before publishing.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>In this step-by-step tutorial, we&#8217;ll share an easy way to use a Google snippet preview to optimize your SEO. And we&#8217;ll provide some snippet tips that&#8217;ll put you ahead of the game.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"is-layout-flow wp-block-group aioseo-table-of-contents has-theme-info-background-color has-background\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>In This Article</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-aioseo-table-of-contents\"><ul><li><a href=\"#aioseo-why-use-a-google-snippet-preview\">Why Use a Google Snippet Preview?</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-step-1-download-the-all-in-one-seo-aioseo-plugin\">Step 1: Download the All in One SEO (AIOSEO) Plugin</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-step-2-find-the-google-snippet-preview\">Step 2: Find the Google Snippet Preview</a><ul></ul></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-step-3-optimize-your-title\">Step 3: Optimize Your Title</a><ul></ul></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-step-4-optimize-your-description\">Step 4: Optimize Your Description</a><ul></ul></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-step-5-optimize-your-slug\">Step 5: Optimize Your Slug</a><ul></ul></li></ul></div>\n</div></div>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"aioseo-why-use-a-google-snippet-preview\">Why Use a Google Snippet Preview?</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>We all know how standard search engine results look. There&#8217;s a title, a link, and a description. In SEO, we call that a &#8220;search snippet.&#8221; It looks like this:</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"918\" height=\"208\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/google-search-snippet.png\" alt=\"standard google search snippet\" class=\"wp-image-180522\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/google-search-snippet.png 918w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/google-search-snippet-300x68.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/google-search-snippet-768x174.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/google-search-snippet-600x136.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/google-search-snippet-190x43.png 190w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/google-search-snippet-397x90.png 397w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>But sometimes, the title gets cut off, as in this example below.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"233\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/11-serp-title-truncated-1024x233.png\" alt=\"truncated title in serp\" class=\"wp-image-177440\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/11-serp-title-truncated-1024x233.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/11-serp-title-truncated-300x68.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/11-serp-title-truncated-768x174.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/11-serp-title-truncated-600x136.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/11-serp-title-truncated-190x43.png 190w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/11-serp-title-truncated-396x90.png 396w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/11-serp-title-truncated.png 1206w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Or the snippet may not provide a clear description of the article.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Problems like this can cause people to skip your article. And that makes it hard to get new readers or sales.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Previews provide a simple way to improve your snippet so that it drives more click-throughs.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>And one of the easiest ways to access and edit previews is to use an <strong>SEO plugin</strong>.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"aioseo-step-1-download-the-all-in-one-seo-aioseo-plugin\">Step 1: Download the All in One SEO (AIOSEO) Plugin</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>We recommend you download and install the <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/pricing\">All in One SEO (AIOSEO) plugin</a>. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>This is an established plugin that&#8217;s beginner-friendly. <br><br>All in One SEO (AIOSEO) has thousands of 5-star ratings on WordPress.org, and over 3 million people are currently using it.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"485\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/aioseo-homepage-1024x485.png\" alt=\"aioseo homepage\" class=\"wp-image-140989\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/aioseo-homepage-1024x485.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/aioseo-homepage-300x142.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/aioseo-homepage-768x364.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/aioseo-homepage-600x284.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/aioseo-homepage-127x60.png 127w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/aioseo-homepage-190x90.png 190w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/aioseo-homepage.png 1260w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>After downloading AIOSEO in your WordPress editor:</p>\n\n\n\n<ol>\n<li>Go to <strong>Plugins » Add New</strong></li>\n\n\n\n<li>Upload the zip file</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Click <strong>Activate</strong></li>\n</ol>\n\n\n\n<p>A setup wizard will open and walk you through a few easy steps.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Questions? Check out our<a href=\"https://aioseo.com/docs/installation-instructions-for-wordpress-com-users/\"> installation guide</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"aioseo-step-2-find-the-google-snippet-preview\">Step 2: Find the Google Snippet Preview</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Now, in your WordPress editor, navigate to a page or post that you want to see a Google snippet preview of.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-option-1-start-from-wordpress-preview-mode\">Option 1: Start From WordPress Preview Mode</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>If you’re in WordPress preview mode, hover your mouse over the AIOSEO icon in the admin bar.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>In the drop-down that appears, select <strong>SEO Preview</strong>.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1022\" height=\"244\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/3-aioseo-seo-preview-1.png\" alt=\"aioseo seo preview menu\" class=\"wp-image-180526\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/3-aioseo-seo-preview-1.png 1022w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/3-aioseo-seo-preview-1-300x72.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/3-aioseo-seo-preview-1-768x183.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/3-aioseo-seo-preview-1-600x143.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/3-aioseo-seo-preview-1-190x45.png 190w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/3-aioseo-seo-preview-1-377x90.png 377w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Now you can see your Google SERP snippet preview:<br></p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"574\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/4-SEO-preview-window-1024x574.png\" alt=\"aioseo google snippet preview\" class=\"wp-image-177332\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/4-SEO-preview-window-1024x574.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/4-SEO-preview-window-300x168.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/4-SEO-preview-window-768x431.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/4-SEO-preview-window-704x396.png 704w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/4-SEO-preview-window-600x336.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/4-SEO-preview-window-107x60.png 107w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/4-SEO-preview-window-160x90.png 160w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/4-SEO-preview-window.png 1118w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>If you want to change your title or description, click the gray <strong>Edit Snippet</strong> button. Then follow the instructions in <strong>Steps 2</strong> and <strong>3</strong>.<br></p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-option-2-start-from-editing-mode\">Option 2: Start From Editing Mode</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>If you’re in <strong>WordPress editing mode</strong>, do the following.</p>\n\n\n\n<ol>\n<li>In the upper right corner, click on the <strong>AIOSEO button</strong>. (That will open AIOSEO settings in your right-hand navigation column.)</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Then click <strong>General.</strong></li>\n</ol>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"725\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/5-aioseo-find-google-snippet-preview-1024x725.png\" alt=\"aioseo settings\" class=\"wp-image-177334\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/5-aioseo-find-google-snippet-preview-1024x725.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/5-aioseo-find-google-snippet-preview-300x212.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/5-aioseo-find-google-snippet-preview-768x544.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/5-aioseo-find-google-snippet-preview-600x425.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/5-aioseo-find-google-snippet-preview-85x60.png 85w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/5-aioseo-find-google-snippet-preview-127x90.png 127w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/5-aioseo-find-google-snippet-preview.png 1040w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Now you&#8217;ll see your Google snippet preview.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"435\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/aioseo-snippet-preview-right-column-1024x435.jpg\" alt=\"aioseo google snippet preview sidebar\" class=\"wp-image-177456\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/aioseo-snippet-preview-right-column-1024x435.jpg 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/aioseo-snippet-preview-right-column-300x127.jpg 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/aioseo-snippet-preview-right-column-768x326.jpg 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/aioseo-snippet-preview-right-column-1536x653.jpg 1536w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/aioseo-snippet-preview-right-column-2048x870.jpg 2048w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/aioseo-snippet-preview-right-column-600x255.jpg 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/aioseo-snippet-preview-right-column-141x60.jpg 141w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/aioseo-snippet-preview-right-column-212x90.jpg 212w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>This snippet preview is narrow and simulates what your article would look like on a smartphone.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-how-to-toggle-between-the-desktop-and-mobile-preview\">How to Toggle Between the Desktop and Mobile Preview</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Beneath the snippet preview, click the edit button to see a desktop preview.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"646\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/6-edit-google-snippet-preview-1024x646.jpg\" alt=\"aioseo edit google snippet preview\" class=\"wp-image-177333\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/6-edit-google-snippet-preview-1024x646.jpg 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/6-edit-google-snippet-preview-300x189.jpg 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/6-edit-google-snippet-preview-768x485.jpg 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/6-edit-google-snippet-preview-600x379.jpg 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/6-edit-google-snippet-preview-95x60.jpg 95w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/6-edit-google-snippet-preview-143x90.jpg 143w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/6-edit-google-snippet-preview.jpg 1090w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>A small pop-up window will appear. Notice that your snippet preview is wider. The preview is now simulating what your page would look like for someone doing a desktop Google search.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"487\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/7-desktop-google-snippet-preview-1024x487.png\" alt=\"aioseo google snippet preview desktop mode\" class=\"wp-image-177335\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/7-desktop-google-snippet-preview-1024x487.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/7-desktop-google-snippet-preview-300x143.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/7-desktop-google-snippet-preview-768x365.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/7-desktop-google-snippet-preview-600x285.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/7-desktop-google-snippet-preview-126x60.png 126w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/7-desktop-google-snippet-preview-189x90.png 189w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/7-desktop-google-snippet-preview.png 1117w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>You can toggle between desktop and mobile snippet previews by clicking the device icons in the upper right area of the pop-up window.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"477\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/8-toggle-google-snippet-preview-1024x477.png\" alt=\"google snippet preview device toggle \" class=\"wp-image-177336\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/8-toggle-google-snippet-preview-1024x477.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/8-toggle-google-snippet-preview-300x140.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/8-toggle-google-snippet-preview-768x358.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/8-toggle-google-snippet-preview-600x280.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/8-toggle-google-snippet-preview-129x60.png 129w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/8-toggle-google-snippet-preview-193x90.png 193w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/8-toggle-google-snippet-preview.png 1105w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Now that you know where to find the Google snippet preview let&#8217;s explore the <strong>Post Title</strong> field.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"aioseo-step-3-optimize-your-title\">Step 3: Optimize Your Title</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Below the Google snippet preview, you&#8217;ll see a <strong>Post</strong> <strong>Title</strong> section.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Here’s how it looks.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"952\" height=\"312\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/aioseo-post-title-field.png\" alt=\"aioseo preview snippet editor\" class=\"wp-image-180529\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/aioseo-post-title-field.png 952w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/aioseo-post-title-field-300x98.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/aioseo-post-title-field-768x252.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/aioseo-post-title-field-600x197.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/aioseo-post-title-field-183x60.png 183w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/aioseo-post-title-field-275x90.png 275w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>You&#8217;ll see 3 small gray boxes (or &#8220;tags&#8221;) in the Post Title field.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"952\" height=\"293\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/aioseo-post-title-tags.png\" alt=\"aioseo post title tags\" class=\"wp-image-180527\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/aioseo-post-title-tags.png 952w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/aioseo-post-title-tags-300x92.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/aioseo-post-title-tags-768x236.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/aioseo-post-title-tags-600x185.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/aioseo-post-title-tags-190x58.png 190w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/aioseo-post-title-tags-292x90.png 292w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Here&#8217;s what those gray tags do.</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>The <strong>Post Title </strong>tag automatically pulls in the title you typed at the top of your article.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>The <strong>Separator </strong>tag automatically adds a customizable separator character (like a dash or a pipe) after your title.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>The <strong>Site Title</strong> tag automatically pulls in the name of your website.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>These tags can save time because you don&#8217;t need to type any content in.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>By default in AIOSEO, this is how all your Post Title fields are set up.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>But you can remove the <strong>Site Title</strong> and <strong>Separator</strong> and use all 60 characters just for your article title.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Now, let&#8217;s look at two cases where you might want to change the default settings of the Post Title.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-case-1-you-want-to-shorten-your-title\">Case #1: You Want to Shorten Your Title</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>In our example preview below, our title is over the recommended 60 characters. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Note that the <strong>Separator</strong> and <strong>Site Title</strong> (plus the spaces in between) are part of that 60-character count.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"641\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/12-title-over-recommended-character-limit-1024x641.png\" alt=\"aioseo post title over character limit\" class=\"wp-image-177441\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/12-title-over-recommended-character-limit-1024x641.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/12-title-over-recommended-character-limit-300x188.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/12-title-over-recommended-character-limit-768x480.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/12-title-over-recommended-character-limit-600x375.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/12-title-over-recommended-character-limit-96x60.png 96w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/12-title-over-recommended-character-limit-144x90.png 144w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/12-title-over-recommended-character-limit.png 1111w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>So, what to do?</p>\n\n\n\n<p>You could remove the <strong>Separator</strong> and <strong>Site Title</strong> tags. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>(You can always add them by clicking the &#8220;spares&#8221; at the upper right.)</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"949\" height=\"550\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/aioseo-preview-snippet-editor.png\" alt=\"aioseo post title tag removal\" class=\"wp-image-180532\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/aioseo-preview-snippet-editor.png 949w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/aioseo-preview-snippet-editor-300x174.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/aioseo-preview-snippet-editor-768x445.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/aioseo-preview-snippet-editor-600x348.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/aioseo-preview-snippet-editor-104x60.png 104w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/aioseo-preview-snippet-editor-155x90.png 155w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Notice in the example above that our title is still over the recommended 60 characters.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>By removing the word &#8220;Downloadable,&#8221; our title now fits within the recommendations.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Note: to change your title, either edit the title directly on the article page, or, delete the gray Post Title tag from the field, and type in your preferred title.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>We did the latter in this case below:</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"950\" height=\"492\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/aioseo-post-title-under-60.png\" alt=\"aioseo post title under character limit\" class=\"wp-image-180533\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/aioseo-post-title-under-60.png 950w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/aioseo-post-title-under-60-300x155.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/aioseo-post-title-under-60-768x398.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/aioseo-post-title-under-60-600x311.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/aioseo-post-title-under-60-116x60.png 116w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/aioseo-post-title-under-60-174x90.png 174w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-case-2-we-want-to-use-all-available-space-for-our-title\">Case #2: We want to use all available space for our title</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Now let&#8217;s imagine that our title, separator, and site title combined are within the recommended 60-character limit. Here&#8217;s a made-up example:</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>How to Replace a Toilet (5 steps) &#8211; Monongahela Hardware</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p>But the site name takes up a lot of space.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>We might want to get rid of the separator and site title just so we can add more words to our title, like so:</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\"><strong>How to Replace a Toilet (5 steps) &#8211; [DIY or Hire us]</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p>The headline above gives the searcher more information: It&#8217;s not just a DIY article. You can hire this hardware store to do this job for you.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-aioseo-theme-notice-box\" role=\"alert\">\n<p>If the site owner has set up <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/a-complete-local-seo-checklist/\">local SEO</a>, then this article will show up for local searches for &#8220;how to replace a toilet.&#8221;</p>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<p>Now you understand the default settings for the Post Title field. And you know you can change these or manually type in a title.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Let&#8217;s take a look at exactly how your title affects SEO.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-title-seo-factors\">Title SEO Factors</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Titles can have a significant impact on click-through rates. Here are 3 ways to prep your title for SEO.</p>\n\n\n\n<h4 id=\"aioseo-include-a-focus-keyword\">Include a Focus Keyword</h4>\n\n\n\n<p>It&#8217;s important to include your <strong>focus keyword </strong>in your SEO title.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Your <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/docs/using-the-focus-keyphrase-to-analyze-your-content/\">focus keyword</a> helps Google understand what search queries your article should appear in.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>You can think of the focus keyword as the <strong>main topic</strong> of your article. (New to keyword research? Check out this great <a href=\"https://www.blogtyrant.com/how-to-easily-find-the-best-keywords/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" title=\"\">beginner&#8217;s guide</a>.)</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Here are some examples of focus keywords included in titles.</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>8 Best <span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">WordPress FAQ Block</span> Plugins</li>\n\n\n\n<li><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Go Paperless</span> in 7 Steps</li>\n\n\n\n<li>9 Best <span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Clickfunnels Replacements</span> Free and Paid</li>\n\n\n\n<li><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">OptinMonster Review</span> 2023: Is it the Best Tool for Growth?</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h4 id=\"aioseo-persuasive-text\">Persuasive Text</h4>\n\n\n\n<p>Your title should be clear and descriptive. Along with the page description (discussed below), your title is one of your biggest opportunities to get click-throughs. It should give searchers an excellent reason to click.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>But don&#8217;t over-promise. Write a title that tells the searcher what they can expect from your web page.</p>\n\n\n\n<h4 id=\"aioseo-title-length-is-the-number-of-characters-important\">Title Length: Is the Number of Characters Important?</h4>\n\n\n\n<p>We mentioned that the AIOSEO snippet preview tool recommends capping titles at 60 characters.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>But here&#8217;s some nuance. There are cases where you may want to use titles that are <strong>longer</strong>. Marketers often do.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Let&#8217;s see why. In the example below, this article has a 66-character-long title. The article is displayed as a &#8220;featured snippet.&#8221; Because of the large display area, the full title is shown (at the top).</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"954\" height=\"510\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/featured-snippet-title-length.png\" alt=\"featured snippet example\" class=\"wp-image-180535\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/featured-snippet-title-length.png 954w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/featured-snippet-title-length-300x160.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/featured-snippet-title-length-768x411.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/featured-snippet-title-length-600x321.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/featured-snippet-title-length-112x60.png 112w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/featured-snippet-title-length-168x90.png 168w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>But only some articles wind up as featured snippets. The key benefit of using a long title is you can <strong>include additional keywords</strong> for search engines.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you try this, make sure that what appears in the first 60 or so characters is a complete title.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Now, let&#8217;s move on to your description.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"aioseo-step-4-optimize-your-description\">Step 4: Optimize Your Description</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Returning to the Google snippet preview, scroll past the <strong>Post Title,</strong> and you&#8217;ll see a <strong>Meta Description</strong> area.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Here we recommend that you remove the <strong>Excerpt</strong> tag. It&#8217;s just a placeholder that tells Google to pull any excerpt from your page.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Because you get 160 characters for your description, you&#8217;ll want to craft it yourself.</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Be sure to include your focus keyword.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Try to include a few related keywords.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>In the example below, &#8220;create a digital strategy&#8221; is our focus keyword (or main article topic). We&#8217;ve added the words &#8220;traffic, conversions, and revenue&#8221; because these are 3 things people hope to achieve with a digital strategy.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Then we added some &#8220;bonus&#8221; information at the end.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"347\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/aioseo-optimize-meta-description-1024x347.png\" alt=\"aioseo meta description field\" class=\"wp-image-180536\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/aioseo-optimize-meta-description-1024x347.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/aioseo-optimize-meta-description-300x102.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/aioseo-optimize-meta-description-768x261.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/aioseo-optimize-meta-description-600x204.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/aioseo-optimize-meta-description-177x60.png 177w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/aioseo-optimize-meta-description-265x90.png 265w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/aioseo-optimize-meta-description.png 1117w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-meta-description-seo-factors\">Meta Description SEO Factors</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Now let&#8217;s review the main SEO factors for your meta description. It’s important to realize that meta descriptions are not ranking factors, but they can boost your SEO.</p>\n\n\n\n<h4 id=\"aioseo-focus-keyword-presence\">Focus Keyword Presence</h4>\n\n\n\n<p>Your focus keyword should be in your meta description. And you can include related keywords.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>You can find related keywords by doing a Chrome Incognito search using your focus keyword or by using a free tool like Ubersuggest.</p>\n\n\n\n<h4 id=\"aioseo-informative-and-persuasive-text\">Informative and Persuasive Text</h4>\n\n\n\n<p>Ask yourself: “What’s unique or valuable about my article? How is it different from others on the same subject?</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Like your title, this is a significant opportunity to win click-throughs with a precise summary.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-emojis\">Emojis</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>You can put <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-add-emojis-to-your-wordpress-blog/\">emojis</a> in your meta description or title. Emojis aren’t a ranking factor, but they are eye-catching. For that reason, they may increase click-throughs.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>You’ll need to experiment to see if this is the case with your content. But make sure emojis are a good fit with your brand voice first.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"193\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/emojis-in-serp-title-1024x193.png\" alt=\"emoji in search snippet \" class=\"wp-image-180538\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/emojis-in-serp-title-1024x193.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/emojis-in-serp-title-300x57.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/emojis-in-serp-title-768x145.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/emojis-in-serp-title-600x113.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/emojis-in-serp-title-190x36.png 190w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/emojis-in-serp-title-477x90.png 477w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/emojis-in-serp-title.png 1113w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"aioseo-step-5-optimize-your-slug\">Step 5: Optimize Your Slug</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>A slug is the last part of a URL. A forward slash precedes it:</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\">example.com/blog/<strong>hello-world</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p>In the example above, &#8220;hello-world&#8221; is the slug.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>By default, WordPress automatically generates a slug for each post you create. It simply copies the title of your post. So a post called &#8220;This is My First Blog Post&#8221; would generate this slug:</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\">example.com/blog/<strong>this-is-my-first-blog-post</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-include-your-focus-keyword\">Include Your Focus Keyword</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>We recommend that you include your focus keyword in your slug.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>You&#8217;ll be fine if you include your keyword in the title. But if you want to edit your slug, you can click the gear icon at the upper right. Then go to <strong>Post » Permalink.</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p>You&#8217;ll see a URL slug field. Just type your preferred slug there.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"401\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/wordpress-edit-url-slug-1024x401.png\" alt=\"wordpress edit url slug\" class=\"wp-image-180539\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/wordpress-edit-url-slug-1024x401.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/wordpress-edit-url-slug-300x118.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/wordpress-edit-url-slug-768x301.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/wordpress-edit-url-slug-600x235.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/wordpress-edit-url-slug-153x60.png 153w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/wordpress-edit-url-slug-230x90.png 230w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/wordpress-edit-url-slug.png 1105w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"aioseo-a-few-extra-notes\">A Few Extra Notes</h2>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><strong>SEO tools: </strong>Now that you’re using the All in One SEO (AIOSEO) plugin, explore some easy SEO wins like <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/docs/adding-breadcrumbs-to-your-site-using-the-aioseo-breadcrumbs-block/\" title=\"\">adding breadcrumbs</a> or a <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/wordpress-table-of-contents-seo/#aioseo-quick-start-guide-add-a-table-of-contents-now\" title=\"\">table of contents</a> to your pages. That can improve user experience too.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Pixels</strong>: Some websites say you need to measure your titles by pixels. This isn&#8217;t true. It&#8217;s a rumor that spread after a Google employee made a related <a href=\"https://twitter.com/danbri/status/1376808127241289730\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">joke</a>.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>What’s Google SERP?</strong> SERP (or SERPs) stands for search engine results pages. Put “Google” in front of that and the phrase refers specifically to Google’s search engine results pages.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>What’s a SERP simulator</strong>? This is the same thing as a Google snippet preview. There are lots of names for this including SERP snippet preview tool or Google SERP snippet optimization tool. </li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"aioseo-whats-next\">What&#8217;s Next?</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Small tweaks to your title and description can have an outsized impact.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>We hope this post helped you understand the benefit of using the AIOSEO plugin to optimize Google snippet previews in WordPress.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>And check out our article on <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/small-business-seo-scams-how-to-detect-and-avoid-them/\" title=\"\">how to avoid SEO scams</a> and <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-use-a-wordpress-faq-block-to-boost-seo-and-get-more-traffic/\" title=\"\">how to use FAQs strategically</a> to drive more traffic.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you found this article helpful, then please subscribe to our <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/c/AIOSEO\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">YouTube Channel</a>. You’ll find many more helpful tutorials there. You can also follow us on <a href=\"https://twitter.com/aioseopack\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">Twitter</a>, <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/company/aioseo/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">LinkedIn</a>, or <a href=\"https://facebook.com/aioseopack/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">Facebook</a> to stay in the loop.</p>The post <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-use-google-snippet-preview-to-boost-seo/\">How to Use the Google Snippet Preview to Boost Your SEO</a> first appeared on <a href=\"https://aioseo.com\">AIOSEO</a>.\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:71:\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-use-google-snippet-preview-to-boost-seo/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:1;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:82:\"\n		\n		\n					\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n					\n										\n					\n					\n			\n		\n		\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4