a\";s:4:\"Blog\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:26:\"Broken link checker plugin\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:16:\"Fix broken links\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:28:\"https://aioseo.com/?p=174466\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:440:\"<p>Are you losing traffic due to broken links? Do you know if you have any broken links? Surprisingly, most links on the web are broken. There’s even a name for it: link rot. So, why does it matter? Broken links&#8230;</p>\nThe post <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/announcing-broken-link-checker-plugin/\">Announcing Broken Link Checker: Find and Fix Broken Links to Boost Your SEO</a> first appeared on <a href=\"https://aioseo.com\">AIOSEO</a>.\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Benjamin Rojas\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9811:\"<p>Are you losing traffic due to broken links? Do you know if you have any broken links?</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Surprisingly, most links on the web <em>are</em> broken. There’s even a name for it: <strong>link rot</strong>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>So, why does it matter?</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Broken links make it hard for users to find what they’re looking for. That drives visitors away. And when you lose visitors, you lose conversions and sales.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>A broken link can also make a page invisible to search engines. That means zero traffic.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>But who has time to check every web page and link on a website? Ideally, site owners should check for broken links regularly. But that makes the task even more time-consuming.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>That’s why we decided to create a fast solution that even a beginner can use.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"is-layout-flow wp-block-group aioseo-table-of-contents has-theme-info-background-color has-background\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>In This Article</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-aioseo-table-of-contents\"><ul><li><a href=\"#aioseo-find-and-fix-broken-links-easily\">Find and Fix Broken Links, Easily</a><ul><li><a href=\"#aioseo-semi-weekly-scans\">Semi-Weekly Scans</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-additional-features\">Additional Features</a></li></ul></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-control-which-types-of-pages-are-scanned\">Control Which Types of Pages are Scanned</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-scanning-the-right-way\">Scanning &#8211; the Right Way</a><ul><li><a href=\"#aioseo-avoid-being-blacklisted\">Avoid Being Blacklisted</a></li></ul></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-how-to-get-broken-link-checker-by-aioseo\">How to Get Broken Link Checker by AIOSEO</a></li></ul></div>\n</div></div>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"aioseo-find-and-fix-broken-links-easily\">Find and Fix Broken Links, Easily</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>We’re excited to announce our brand new, standalone <strong><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/pricing-broken-link-checker/\" title=\"Broken Link Checker plugin\">Broken Link Checker plugin</a></strong>.</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>This plugin <strong><em>scans</em></strong> all the links on your site.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Then it <strong><em>lists</em></strong> all broken links and provides an <strong>easy way to fix</strong> them.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>You don’t even need to open any web pages.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Just click <strong>Edit URL</strong> to replace a broken link – right inside the plugin.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"523\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/fix-broken-link-1024x523.png\" alt=\"broken link checker edit url\" class=\"wp-image-174472\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/fix-broken-link-1024x523.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/fix-broken-link-300x153.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/fix-broken-link-768x392.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/fix-broken-link-1536x784.png 1536w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/fix-broken-link-2048x1046.png 2048w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/fix-broken-link-600x306.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/fix-broken-link-118x60.png 118w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/fix-broken-link-176x90.png 176w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>You can also edit the anchor text at the same time.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-semi-weekly-scans\">Semi-Weekly Scans</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>The Broken Link Checker plugin automatically scans your site <strong>every 3 days</strong>. So there’s no need to worry about missing broken links in the future.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-additional-features\">Additional Features</h3>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>You can opt to view <strong>Broken links</strong>, <strong>Redirects</strong>, or <strong>All</strong> links on your site.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Click <strong>Unlink</strong> to remove a link.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Click <strong>Recheck</strong> to re-scan a link.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Webmasters and SEO professionals will appreciate the scrollable <strong>Status Details</strong> window that displays response headers and other information for each link.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"763\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/broken-link-checker-status-details-1024x763.png\" alt=\"broken link checker status details\" class=\"wp-image-174473\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/broken-link-checker-status-details-1024x763.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/broken-link-checker-status-details-300x223.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/broken-link-checker-status-details-768x572.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/broken-link-checker-status-details-600x447.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/broken-link-checker-status-details-81x60.png 81w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/broken-link-checker-status-details-121x90.png 121w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/broken-link-checker-status-details.png 1509w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"aioseo-control-which-types-of-pages-are-scanned\">Control Which Types of Pages are Scanned</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Our advanced settings give you full control over which pages get scanned.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Include or exclude:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Specific, named posts</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Scheduled posts</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Drafts or published posts</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Private posts.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"578\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/broken-link-checker-advanced-settings-1024x578.png\" alt=\"broken link checker advanced settings\" class=\"wp-image-174470\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/broken-link-checker-advanced-settings-1024x578.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/broken-link-checker-advanced-settings-300x169.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/broken-link-checker-advanced-settings-768x434.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/broken-link-checker-advanced-settings-704x396.png 704w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/broken-link-checker-advanced-settings-600x339.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/broken-link-checker-advanced-settings-106x60.png 106w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/broken-link-checker-advanced-settings-159x90.png 159w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/broken-link-checker-advanced-settings.png 1341w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"aioseo-scanning-the-right-way\">Scanning &#8211; the Right Way</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>As mentioned, we scan <em>external</em> links (links from your website to others) as well as internal links (links from one page on your site to another page on your site).</p>\n\n\n\n<p>To protect your site, we pay for an<strong> external server </strong>to do this scanning (also called “pinging”). That means any external links you have on your site are pinged by us <em>from our </em><strong><em>private web server.</em></strong></p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-avoid-being-blacklisted\">Avoid Being Blacklisted</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Most of our competitors don’t use an external server. They do their pinging directly from their clients’ sites. That puts those sites at risk of being <em>blacklisted</em>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The blacklisting occurs because when a website is used to ping external sites <em>repeatedly</em>, that behavior looks suspicious to internet service providers.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"aioseo-how-to-get-broken-link-checker-by-aioseo\">How to Get Broken Link Checker by AIOSEO</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>You can download <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/pricing-broken-link-checker/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"Broken Link Checker by AIOSEO\"><strong>Broken Link Checker by AIOSEO</strong> here</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"456\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/wordpress-broken-link-checker-plugin-1024x456.png\" alt=\"aioseo broken link checker plugin\" class=\"wp-image-174725\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/wordpress-broken-link-checker-plugin-1024x456.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/wordpress-broken-link-checker-plugin-300x134.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/wordpress-broken-link-checker-plugin-768x342.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/wordpress-broken-link-checker-plugin-600x267.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/wordpress-broken-link-checker-plugin-135x60.png 135w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/wordpress-broken-link-checker-plugin-202x90.png 202w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/wordpress-broken-link-checker-plugin.png 1246w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>And if you’re not yet using the All in One SEO plugin, <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/pricing/\">download that here</a> so you can improve your SEO. And see our product <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/changelog\">changelog</a> for recent updates.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>We appreciate all of your feedback. Please keep sharing your ideas with us!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Keep an eye on our blog, too. Soon we’ll publish additional tutorials on how to use the new Broken Link Checker plugin.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>And if you have questions about the new plugin, please reach out to our <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/contact/\">customer support</a> team. Or drop a comment below.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>We’re delighted to support your success with new tools like Broken Link Checker!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>– <em>Benjamin Rojas<br>President of AIOSEO</em></p>The post <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/announcing-broken-link-checker-plugin/\">Announcing Broken Link Checker: Find and Fix Broken Links to Boost Your SEO</a> first appeared on <a href=\"https://aioseo.com\">AIOSEO</a>.\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:62:\"https://aioseo.com/announcing-broken-link-checker-plugin/feed/\