/p>\n\n\n\n<p>In this article, we’ll show you how to use AI SEO software tools to boost your rankings.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"is-layout-flow wp-block-group aioseo-table-of-contents has-theme-info-background-color has-background\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>In This Article</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-aioseo-table-of-contents\"><ul><li><a href=\"#aioseo-what-is-ai-seo\">What is AI SEO?</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-how-to-use-ai-seo-software-to-boost-your-search-rankings\">How to Use AI SEO Software to Boost Your Search Rankings</a><ul><li><a href=\"#aioseo-1-use-the-right-ai-seo-tools\">1. Use the Right AI SEO Software</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-2-boost-organic-ctr-on-serps-using-ai\">2. Boost Organic CTR on SERPs Using AI Software</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-3-build-internal-links-for-topical-authority-and-better-rankings\">3. Build Internal Links for Topical Authority and Better Rankings</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-4-discover-hidden-ranking-opportunities\">4. Discover Hidden Ranking Opportunities</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-5-optimize-your-content-more-effectively\">5. Optimize Your Content More Effectively</a></li></ul></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-ai-seo-software-giving-you-the-edge-you-need-to-outrank-your-competitors\">AI SEO Software: Giving You the Edge You Need to Outrank Your Competitors</a></li></ul></div>\n</div></div>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"aioseo-what-is-ai-seo\">What is AI SEO?</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>To best understand AI SEO (not to be confused with AIOSEO), let&#8217;s briefly examine what these 2 acronyms mean.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Artificial intelligence (AI) is an umbrella term that covers several different technologies, including machine learning (ML), natural language processing (NLP), deep learning, computer vision and other emerging technologies. These technologies are designed to help machines perform specific cognitive tasks as well as or better than humans.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>On the other hand, search engine optimization (SEO) enhances your website and web pages to drive free organic traffic from search engines like Google. With SEO, your goal is to follow <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/seo-best-practices/\" title=\"SEO Best Practices: 20 Ultimate SEO Tips to Boost Rankings\">WordPress SEO best practices</a> on your site. Doing so helps search engines easily discover your content and display it in the search results.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>AI SEO, therefore, is using AI technology to optimize your website and content for search engines and users. Doing so helps you easily scale your SEO campaigns and execute tasks faster and more efficiently. As a result, your chances of ranking high on <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/what-are-serps/\" title=\"What Are SERPs (And Why Are they Important to SEO)?\">search engine results pages</a> (SERPs) are bolstered.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"aioseo-how-to-use-ai-seo-software-to-boost-your-search-rankings\">How to Use AI SEO Software to Boost Your Search Rankings</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Now that you know what AI SEO is and its benefits, let’s quickly look at ways you can use it to boost your search rankings.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-1-use-the-right-ai-seo-tools\">1. Use the Right AI SEO Software</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>First, to boost your SEO using AI, you must use the right <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/best-ai-seo-tools-for-wordpress/\" title=\"The 7 Best AI SEO Tools for WordPress in 2023\">AI SEO software</a>. A great example is <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/pricing/\" title=\"Pricing\">All In One SEO</a> (AIOSEO).</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"700\" height=\"311\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/aioseo.png\" alt=\"AIOSEO is one of the best SEO plugins on the market.\" class=\"wp-image-170372\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/aioseo.png 700w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/aioseo-300x133.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/aioseo-600x267.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/aioseo-135x60.png 135w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/aioseo-203x90.png 203w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/pricing/\" title=\"Pricing\">AIOSEO</a> is the best WordPress SEO plugin on the market and has been downloaded over 100 million times. Millions of savvy website owners and marketers trust the plugin to help them dominate SERPs and drive relevant site traffic. This is because the plugin has many <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/features/\" title=\"Features\">powerful SEO features and modules</a> to help you optimize your website for search engines and users.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Besides being the best WordPress SEO plugin, AIOSEO also boasts powerful AI-powered features to help you easily optimize your site for better search rankings. Examples include the AI Title/Description Generator and Link Assistant, which we’ll discuss in the sections below.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>For step-by-step instructions on how to install AIOSEO, check our <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/docs/installing-all-in-one-seo-pro/\" title=\"Installing All in One SEO Pro\">detailed installation guide</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-2-boost-organic-ctr-on-serps-using-ai\">2. Boost Organic CTR on SERPs Using AI Software</h3>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/ways-to-increase-your-organic-clickthrough-rates/\" title=\"8 Proven Ways to Increase Your Organic Clickthrough Rates\">Boosting your organic clickthrough rate</a> (CTR) on SERPs is a great way to use AI in your SEO campaigns. One of the best ways to do this is to optimize your SEO titles and meta descriptions. This is because these are some of the first elements of your search listing users see on SERPs and impact the way users interact with your search listings.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>AIOSEO’s <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/our-openai-integration-just-got-10x-more-affordable-now-using-chatgpt/\" title=\"Our OpenAI Integration Just Got 10x More Affordable – Now Using ChatGPT!\">AI Title/Description Generator</a> is one of the best AI-powered SEO tools for this.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"699\" height=\"353\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/seo-title-generator-1.png\" alt=\"You can use AI SEO software to craft meta data that can help you boost your CTR.\" class=\"wp-image-174239\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/seo-title-generator-1.png 699w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/seo-title-generator-1-300x152.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/seo-title-generator-1-600x303.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/seo-title-generator-1-119x60.png 119w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/seo-title-generator-1-178x90.png 178w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 699px) 100vw, 699px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>This powerful tool helps you automatically generate SEO titles and meta descriptions, saving you precious time.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>And because these are generated from your content, they’re also optimized for SEO. Plus, you can choose from 5 suggestions, making it easier to get the meta description or SEO title that suits your article best.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"702\" height=\"462\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/meta-description-generator-meta-description-examples.png\" alt=\"Generating meta-descriptions is super easy with AIOSEO\'s AI Title/Description Generator.\" class=\"wp-image-170248\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/meta-description-generator-meta-description-examples.png 702w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/meta-description-generator-meta-description-examples-300x197.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/meta-description-generator-meta-description-examples-600x395.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/meta-description-generator-meta-description-examples-91x60.png 91w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/meta-description-generator-meta-description-examples-137x90.png 137w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 702px) 100vw, 702px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Using AI to automatically generate SEO titles and meta descriptions is a great time saver, especially when you need to do so at scale.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-use-a-meta-description-generator-in-wordpress/\" title=\"How to Use a Meta Description Generator in WordPress\">Check out this article</a> for more details on enabling this powerful feature in AIOSEO.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-3-build-internal-links-for-topical-authority-and-better-rankings\">3. Build Internal Links for Topical Authority and Better Rankings</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Another way to boost your search engine rankings is to build strategic internal links. If your website has many pages, manually doing so can be <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/ways-link-assistant-can-save-you-time-on-internal-and-external-link-building/\" title=\"6 Ways Link Assistant Can Save You Time On Internal Link Building\">laborious and time-consuming</a>.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>And you can solve this problem by using AI to build your internal links automatically.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>This is where AIOSEO’s AI-powered <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/features/internal-link-assistant/\" title=\"Link Assistant\">Link Assistant</a> shines.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>With Link Assistant, you get an overview of all the links on your site via the Links Report.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"700\" height=\"381\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/internal-linking-with-link-assistant-links-report.png\" alt=\"To help boost your internal linking strategy, Link Assistant\" class=\"wp-image-79017\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/internal-linking-with-link-assistant-links-report.png 700w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/internal-linking-with-link-assistant-links-report-300x163.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/internal-linking-with-link-assistant-links-report-600x327.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Link Assistant also shows you linking opportunities and enables you to create links between your posts and pages without opening them in the WordPress Editor. You can even edit the anchor text and optimize your link placement.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"354\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/internal-linking-with-link-assistant-markup-1-1024x354.png\" alt=\"Link Assistant enables you to edit anchor text.\" class=\"wp-image-79022\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/internal-linking-with-link-assistant-markup-1-1024x354.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/internal-linking-with-link-assistant-markup-1-300x104.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/internal-linking-with-link-assistant-markup-1-768x266.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/internal-linking-with-link-assistant-markup-1-600x208.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/internal-linking-with-link-assistant-markup-1.png 1078w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>And if you have orphaned pages on your site, Link Assistant shows these to you and enables you to create links to them.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Building internal links is critical to boosting your SEO as it leads to <a href=\"https://ahrefs.com/blog/topical-authority/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">topical authority</a>. It also makes it easier for search engines to crawl and index your content. Both result in higher rankings.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-use-link-assistant-to-optimize-your-internal-linking-strategy/\" title=\"How to Use Link Assistant to Optimize Your Internal Linking Strategy\">Check out this detailed tutorial</a> for a step-by-step guide on using Link Assistant to boost your SEO.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-4-discover-hidden-ranking-opportunities\">4. Discover Hidden Ranking Opportunities&nbsp;</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Keyword research and content gap discovery are essential to ranking high on SERPs and outranking your competitors. However, finding ranking opportunities is becoming more challenging as SEO has become a very competitive marketing channel.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Again, this is where AI can help you.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Using AI can help you find hidden ranking opportunities much faster than you would by using traditional SEO tools. They can help you find keyword opportunities your competitors are not exploiting, giving you a better chance of outranking them and getting the lion’s share of traffic. They can also help you discover what’s working for the top-ranking content regarding keywords, phrases, and questions that are low-hanging fruit.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>A great example of this is <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/frase-io/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"Frase\">Frase</a>. This powerful AI-powered tool helps you create optimized content briefs designed to help you create content that ranks well.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>So, if you’re looking for a great way to get to the top of the SERPs, use AI SEO software to find hidden ranking opportunities.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-5-optimize-your-content-more-effectively\">5. Optimize Your Content More Effectively</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Content optimization is the process of finetuning your content to stand a better chance of ranking high on SERPs. Doing so manually is laborious, especially when you need to produce a lot of content.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>That’s why you should use AI SEO software to do this.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Examples of AI-powered content optimization tools include Semrush’s <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/semrush-seo-writing-assistant/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"Semrush Writing Assistant\">SEO Writing Assistant</a> and <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/surfer-seo/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"Surfer SEO\">SurferSEO</a>. These will help you know:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Which keywords to include in your content</li>\n\n\n\n<li>&nbsp;The questions users are asking</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Content gaps to exploit</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>This helps you create content that’s easily discoverable by search engines. It also helps ensure your content meets search intent.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"aioseo-ai-seo-software-giving-you-the-edge-you-need-to-outrank-your-competitors\">AI SEO Software: Giving You the Edge You Need to Outrank Your Competitors&nbsp;</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>AI SEO software offers excellent tools for designing and deploying SEO campaigns quickly. As a result, you get to rank faster and drive more traffic to your site.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>We hope this article has helped you learn how to use AI SEO software to boost your rankings. You may also want to check out other articles on our blog, like our <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/ultimate-wordpress-seo-guide/\" title=\"Ultimate WordPress SEO Guide: Optimize Your Site in 2023\">ultimate WordPress SEO guide</a> or our <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/what-is-technical-seo-the-best-checklist-in-2022/\" title=\"What Is Technical SEO? The Best Checklist in 2023\">technical SEO checklist</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you found this article helpful, then please subscribe to our <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/c/AIOSEO\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">YouTube Channel</a>. You’ll find many more helpful tutorials there. You can also follow us on <a href=\"https://twitter.com/aioseopack\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">Twitter</a>, <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/company/aioseo/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">LinkedIn</a>, or <a href=\"https://facebook.com/aioseopack/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">Facebook</a> to stay in the loop.</p>The post <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-use-ai-seo-software-to-boost-rankings/\">How to Use AI SEO Software to Boost Your Rankings</a> first appeared on <a href=\"https://aioseo.com\">AIOSEO</a>.\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:69:\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-use-ai-seo-software-to-boost-rankings/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"2\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:7;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:85:\"\n		\n		\n					\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n					\n										\n					\n					\n			\n		\n		\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:68:\"How to Manage Google Reviews for Improved SEO (Small Business Guide)\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:154:\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-manage-google-reviews-for-improved-seo/?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=how-to-manage-google-reviews-for-improved-seo\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:73:\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-manage-google-reviews-for-improved-seo/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Wed, 29 Mar 2023 20:24:11 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:5:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:4:\"Blog\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:8:\"SEO Tips\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Google Reviews\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:28:\"How to manage Google Reviews\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:4;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"local seo\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:28:\"https://aioseo.com/?p=172962\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:470:\"<p>Wondering how to manage Google Reviews to boost your SEO and business reputation? The majority of consumers use Google Reviews to make buying decisions. The good news is there are easy steps business owners can take to ensure these reviews&#8230;</p>\nThe post <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-manage-google-reviews-for-improved-seo/\">How to Manage Google Reviews for Improved SEO (Small Business Guide)</a> first appeared on <a href=\"https://aioseo.com\">AIOSEO</a>.\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:15:\"Sherrie Gossett\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:32946:\"<p>Wondering how to manage Google Reviews to boost your SEO and business reputation?</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The majority of consumers use Google Reviews to make buying decisions. The good news is there are easy steps business owners can take to ensure these reviews make a positive impact.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>In this article, you&#8217;ll learn 3 simple steps to successfully manage Google Reviews.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"is-layout-flow wp-block-group aioseo-table-of-contents has-theme-info-background-color has-background\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>In This Article</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-aioseo-table-of-contents\"><ul><li><a href=\"#aioseo-how-to-find-google-reviews-of-your-business\">How to Find Google Reviews of Your Business</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-create-a-google-business-profile\">Create a Google Business Profile</a><ul></ul></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-how-do-google-reviews-impact-seo\">How Do Google Reviews Impact SEO?</a><ul></ul></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-how-to-manage-google-reviews\">How to Manage Google Reviews</a><ul></ul></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-how-to-get-inappropriate-google-reviews-removed\">Get Inappropriate Google Reviews Removed</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-increase-sales-by-featuring-top-reviews-on-your-website\">Increase Sales</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-make-the-most-of-your-seo-optimize-your-site\">Make the Most of Your SEO: Optimize Your Site</a><ul></ul></li></ul></div>\n</div></div>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"aioseo-how-to-find-google-reviews-of-your-business\">How to Find Google Reviews of Your Business</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>If you already have Google Reviews of your business you&#8217;ll find them by searching for your business name or niche, either in Google or in Google Maps.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"609\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-reviews-maps-1024x609.jpg\" alt=\"star ratings in google maps\" class=\"wp-image-173176\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-reviews-maps-1024x609.jpg 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-reviews-maps-300x179.jpg 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-reviews-maps-768x457.jpg 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-reviews-maps-1536x914.jpg 1536w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-reviews-maps-2048x1219.jpg 2048w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-reviews-maps-600x357.jpg 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-reviews-maps-101x60.jpg 101w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-reviews-maps-151x90.jpg 151w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\"><em>Star ratings for businesses are visible in Google Maps. These are taken from Google Reviews of your business. </em></figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Along with your star rating average and total number of reviews, you can also see a summary of reviews by clicking on your business in Google Maps or by viewing your Google Business Profile. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"665\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-reviews-summary-1024x665.png\" alt=\"google reviews in maps\" class=\"wp-image-173177\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-reviews-summary-1024x665.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-reviews-summary-300x195.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-reviews-summary-768x498.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-reviews-summary-1536x997.png 1536w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-reviews-summary-2048x1329.png 2048w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-reviews-summary-600x389.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-reviews-summary-92x60.png 92w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-reviews-summary-139x90.png 139w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\"><em>In Google Maps, click on a business (like Bistro St-Malo above), to view a summary of related Google Reviews.</em></figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"aioseo-create-a-google-business-profile\">Create a Google Business Profile</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>If you haven&#8217;t already created a Google Business Profile, set one up now. It&#8217;s free. Follow our step-by-step <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-use-a-google-business-profile-to-imrpove-local-seo/\">instructions here</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>A Google Business Profile displays contact and location information for a local business.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>You can add photos, offers, and other details like ecommerce products, and links to book appointments or reservations.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>A star rating average (based on Google Reviews) of your business will also display in your profile, along with review excerpts.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"636\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-business-profile-google-maps-1024x636.jpg\" alt=\"google business profile brasserie blanc\" class=\"wp-image-170751\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-business-profile-google-maps-1024x636.jpg 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-business-profile-google-maps-300x186.jpg 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-business-profile-google-maps-768x477.jpg 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-business-profile-google-maps-1536x954.jpg 1536w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-business-profile-google-maps-2048x1272.jpg 2048w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-business-profile-google-maps-600x373.jpg 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-business-profile-google-maps-97x60.jpg 97w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-business-profile-google-maps-145x90.jpg 145w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-aioseo-theme-notice-box\" role=\"alert\">\n<p>Google Business Profile was formerly called Google My Business (or GMB for short).</p>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-is-a-google-business-profile-important-for-local-seo\">Is a Google Business Profile Important for Local SEO?</h3>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Google <a href=\"https://support.google.com/business/answer/7091\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">recommends</a> a Google Business Profile to improve your local business&#8217;s search engine ranking.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>These profiles are perceived as the single most important local SEO ranking factor, according to a <a href=\"https://whitespark.ca/local-search-ranking-factors/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">recent survey</a> of marketing professionals.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Because of their prominent display, Google Business Profiles can capture the attention and persuade potential customers to patronize your store.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Your Google Business Profile will show up in searches of Google Maps and in the Google Maps app. Notably, the Google Maps app was the<a href=\"https://www.statista.com/statistics/865413/most-popular-us-mapping-apps-ranked-by-audience\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\"><em> </em>most downloaded navigation app</a> last year. This popular Android app is used not only for navigation but for finding places to eat, shop, and play.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-maps-app-mobile-phone-652x1024.jpg\" alt=\"google maps app mobile phone\" class=\"wp-image-172983\" width=\"409\" height=\"768\"/></figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"aioseo-how-do-google-reviews-impact-seo\">How Do Google Reviews Impact SEO?</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Google cites 3 <a href=\"https://support.google.com/business/answer/7091\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">review factors</a> that influence your business&#8217;s ranking in local search results.</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Review score</strong> (star rating average)</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Presence of &#8220;High-quality <strong>positive reviews</strong>&#8220;</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Total number</strong> of reviews.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-impacting-consumer-decisions\">Impacting Consumer Decisions</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Since Google star ratings display across local search results (including Google Maps), their prominence influences people&#8217;s buying decisions.</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.brightlocal.com/research/local-consumer-review-survey-2022/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">85%</a> of searchers consider the <strong>star rating average</strong> of a business to be “important” of “very important.”</li>\n\n\n\n<li>When comparing businesses, 76% of searchers consider which one has the <strong>higher average.</strong></li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https://www.brightlocal.com/research/local-consumer-review-survey-2022/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">73%</a> of local shoppers are swayed by the presence of <strong><em>recent</em></strong> reviews of a business.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"640\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-maps-mister-walker-restaurant-1024x640.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-173183\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-maps-mister-walker-restaurant-1024x640.jpg 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-maps-mister-walker-restaurant-300x187.jpg 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-maps-mister-walker-restaurant-768x480.jpg 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-maps-mister-walker-restaurant-1536x960.jpg 1536w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-maps-mister-walker-restaurant-2048x1279.jpg 2048w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-maps-mister-walker-restaurant-600x375.jpg 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-maps-mister-walker-restaurant-96x60.jpg 96w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-maps-mister-walker-restaurant-144x90.jpg 144w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\"><em>Star ratings appear in many areas of Google Search, including in Google Maps searches.</em></figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"aioseo-how-to-manage-google-reviews\">How to Manage Google Reviews</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Using the SEO and consumer information above, you can adopt a review strategy that emphasizes:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Regularly asking for new reviews.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Increasing your star rating average.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-first-find-the-google-review-link-to-share\">First, Find the Google Review Link to Share</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Anyone who searches for the name of your business will see an option to &#8220;<strong>Write a review</strong>.&#8221; This option is displayed at the top right corner of your Google Business Profile.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"931\" height=\"684\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-business-profile-write-review-button.png\" alt=\"google review write a review \" class=\"wp-image-172985\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-business-profile-write-review-button.png 931w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-business-profile-write-review-button-300x220.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-business-profile-write-review-button-768x564.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-business-profile-write-review-button-600x441.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-business-profile-write-review-button-82x60.png 82w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-business-profile-write-review-button-123x90.png 123w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>But Google also provides local business owners with a <strong>shareable link</strong>. This is useful since you can add it to email messages, on your website, or in live chat messaging with customers.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Here&#8217;s how to get that shareable link.</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Log in to the Gmail account you used to create your Google Business Profile.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Then google your business&#8217;s name.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>At the top of search results you&#8217;ll see options for editing your profile.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Click on <strong>Ask for reviews</strong>.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"498\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/ask-for-google-reviews-1-1024x498.png\" alt=\"manage google reviews\" class=\"wp-image-173187\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/ask-for-google-reviews-1-1024x498.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/ask-for-google-reviews-1-300x146.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/ask-for-google-reviews-1-768x374.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/ask-for-google-reviews-1-600x292.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/ask-for-google-reviews-1-123x60.png 123w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/ask-for-google-reviews-1-185x90.png 185w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/ask-for-google-reviews-1.png 1169w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>That will open a new window. Click <strong>Get more reviews </strong>at the top right.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"377\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/gbp-get-more-reviews-1024x377.png\" alt=\"google get more reviews\" class=\"wp-image-172996\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/gbp-get-more-reviews-1024x377.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/gbp-get-more-reviews-300x110.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/gbp-get-more-reviews-768x283.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/gbp-get-more-reviews-600x221.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/gbp-get-more-reviews-163x60.png 163w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/gbp-get-more-reviews-245x90.png 245w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/gbp-get-more-reviews.png 1296w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Now you&#8217;ll see your shareable <strong>Review link</strong>. Copy it.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"982\" height=\"546\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-review-link.png\" alt=\"google reviews link\" class=\"wp-image-172999\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-review-link.png 982w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-review-link-300x167.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-review-link-768x427.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-review-link-600x334.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-review-link-108x60.png 108w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-review-link-162x90.png 162w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Keep that shareable link somewhere you can easily access it.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Now you&#8217;re ready to plan the next steps.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-ask-for-reviews\">Ask for Reviews</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Regularly asking customers to review you on Google will increase the total number of reviews you have. And it can help sway those searchers who are influenced by<em> recency</em> of reviews.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>To get more customer reviews we recommend that you add requests to your routine business sales and support communications.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Here are some suggestions:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Verbal requests</strong>: Physical stores or businesses that provide local services can have staff work a verbal request into their final face-to-face communication with a customer.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Email requests</strong>: Businesses that routinely obtain the email addresses of their customers can schedule an automated email to go out after a purchase, requesting a review. (<em>Schedule an automated resend of any email that hasn&#8217;t been opened in a set time frame</em>.)</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>In-app notifications</strong>: Software app businesses can add an in-app notification that requests a review.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Physical store displays</strong>: Add window stickers or posters requesting reviews. Google offers a free downloadable <a href=\"https://marketingkit.withgoogle.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">marketing kit</a> with designs for you to use.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"524\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-business-profile-marketing-kit-1024x524.jpg\" alt=\"google business profile marketing kit\" class=\"wp-image-173001\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-business-profile-marketing-kit-1024x524.jpg 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-business-profile-marketing-kit-300x154.jpg 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-business-profile-marketing-kit-768x393.jpg 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-business-profile-marketing-kit-600x307.jpg 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-business-profile-marketing-kit-117x60.jpg 117w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-business-profile-marketing-kit-176x90.jpg 176w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-business-profile-marketing-kit.jpg 1352w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>We recommend that any staff involved in requesting reviews,</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Click the link for themselves so they&#8217;ll be familiar with what customers will see.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Leave a review on a business they&#8217;ve patronized.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>This way, they&#8217;ll be better able to assist customers who have questions.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>You may also want to provide instructions on your website, so you can refer customers there.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-aioseo-theme-notice-box\" role=\"alert\">\n<p>Your customers won&#8217;t need a Gmail account to leave a Google Review. However, they will need a Google account. A Google account is a username and password used to log into Google products like Google Docs, YouTube, or Google Meet video conferencing.</p>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-increase-your-review-score\">Increase Your Review Score</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>We recommend that you set a goal to increase your review score. (This is your star rating average of all reviews.)</p>\n\n\n\n<p>To create focus and get traction,</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Have support or sales staff report (in written and verbal form) the current rating average in your weekly staff meetings.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Regularly track and report at least one other measure of customer satisfaction.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>If need be, improve your customer support process.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>This is a tactic we follow in our own business and it works.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-respond-promptly\">Respond Promptly</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>By responding promptly to reviews you communicate that you care about customer feedback. That can send a positive signal to searchers.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Do follow up on both positive and negative reviews.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Remember:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>People can edit their reviews. After receiving stellar support, that customer may turn a bad review into a good one.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>&#8220;Customers find a mix of positive and negative reviews <strong>more trustworthy</strong>,&#8221; <a href=\"https://support.google.com/business/answer/3474122?hl=en\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">Google reports</a>.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Have a difficult customer that no amount of support will placate? Follow <a href=\"https://www.helpscout.com/blog/firing-a-customer\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" title=\"\">these helpful tips</a> and move on.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"aioseo-how-to-get-inappropriate-google-reviews-removed\">How to Get Inappropriate Google Reviews Removed</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>On occasion someone who&#8217;s not a customer of yours may leave a negative review of your business.</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>They may have mistaken your business for another.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Or they might be a troll.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Follow <a href=\"https://support.google.com/business/answer/4596773\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">these instructions</a> to get Google to remove the review.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"aioseo-increase-sales-by-featuring-top-reviews-on-your-website\">Increase Sales by Featuring Top Reviews on Your Website</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Rave reviews provide prospects with social proof they want before they buy. Embedding top reviews on a website is a proven way to boost sales.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>We recommend that WordPress site owners use the <a href=\"https://smashballoon.com/reviews-feed/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" title=\"\">Smash Balloon plugin</a> to embed online reviews on their website.</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>It takes only a few minutes to set up. (No technical knowledge required.)</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Top reviews will automatically be selected to be shown.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>You can include reviews from other sites like Yelp or Facebook if you like.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Smash Balloon stands out because it&#8217;s optimized for speed, and page speed is an SEO ranking factor. You can also use it to embed social media feeds without bogging down your site.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n<iframe title=\"Embed Reviews on your WordPress Website | Embed Reviews From Google, Facebook, Tripadvisor and Yelp\" width=\"500\" height=\"281\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/RElJPxCIzjo?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n</div></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>We&#8217;ve covered how Google Reviews impact your local SEO. To give yourself every advantage with Google&#8217;s algorithms, you&#8217;ll want to optimize your website too.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"aioseo-make-the-most-of-your-seo-optimize-your-site\">Make the Most of Your SEO: Optimize Your Site</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Google makes it clear that your website ranking impacts how visible your business is in local searches and Google Maps.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>So, in addition to setting up a Google Business Profile, and managing reviews, it&#8217;s wise to optimize your website.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>This is where a plugin like <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/pricing/\">All in One SEO (AIOSEO)</a> comes in. It provides a beginner-friendly way to handle SEO tasks.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"485\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/aioseo-homepage-1024x485.png\" alt=\"aioseo homepage\" class=\"wp-image-140989\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/aioseo-homepage-1024x485.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/aioseo-homepage-300x142.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/aioseo-homepage-768x364.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/aioseo-homepage-600x284.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/aioseo-homepage-127x60.png 127w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/aioseo-homepage-190x90.png 190w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/aioseo-homepage.png 1260w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>All in One SEO makes handling technical SEO tasks simple: you&#8217;ll click some buttons and fill out some forms.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>In addition, AIOSEO provides simple recommendations for improvement of your content.</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Currently, All in One SEO (AIOSEO) is used on over 3 million sites. And it&#8217;s racked up thousands of 5-star ratings on WordPress.org.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Opt for the<a href=\"https://aioseo.com/pricing/\"> Plus or Pro version</a> of the plugin to get the Local SEO features.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-set-up-local-seo-basics\">Set Up Local SEO Basics</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Once you&#8217;ve <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/pricing/\">downloaded</a> and <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/docs/installing-all-in-one-seo-pro/\">installed the plugin</a>, you can set up your local SEO basics. This only takes a few minutes.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>In the left-hand column of your WordPress admin go to <strong>AIOSEO » Local SEO</strong>.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"454\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/aioseo-local-seo-menu-1024x454.jpg\" alt=\"aioseo local seo\" class=\"wp-image-154766\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/aioseo-local-seo-menu-1024x454.jpg 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/aioseo-local-seo-menu-300x133.jpg 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/aioseo-local-seo-menu-768x340.jpg 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/aioseo-local-seo-menu-1536x680.jpg 1536w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/aioseo-local-seo-menu-2048x907.jpg 2048w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/aioseo-local-seo-menu-600x266.jpg 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/aioseo-local-seo-menu-135x60.jpg 135w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/aioseo-local-seo-menu-203x90.jpg 203w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Now you’ll see 3 tabs: one for business location(s), one for opening hours, and one for map.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"478\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/aioseo-local-seo-settings-1024x478.png\" alt=\"aioseo local seo settings\" class=\"wp-image-154770\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/aioseo-local-seo-settings-1024x478.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/aioseo-local-seo-settings-300x140.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/aioseo-local-seo-settings-768x359.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/aioseo-local-seo-settings-600x280.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/aioseo-local-seo-settings-128x60.png 128w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/aioseo-local-seo-settings-193x90.png 193w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/aioseo-local-seo-settings.png 1353w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Click on each tab and fill in the form.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>This local SEO process adds code called <em>schema markup</em> to your website.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>This helps Google understand your business and match it to relevant search queries.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-move-forward-with-on-page-seo\">Move Forward With On-Page SEO</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>The next step is to begin learning how to optimize individual pages, like blog posts, so they rank higher in search engine results.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>All in One SEO (AIOSEO) will make recommendations for each page of your site. Click on the recommendations to get instructions on what to improve.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>We recommend bookmarking the <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/blog/\">AIOSEO blog</a> and <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/c/AIOSEO\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">YouTube channel</a>. Both have plenty of useful tutorials.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"466\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/aioseo-settings-1024x466.png\" alt=\"aioseo general settings\" class=\"wp-image-173004\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/aioseo-settings-1024x466.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/aioseo-settings-300x136.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/aioseo-settings-768x349.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/aioseo-settings-600x273.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/aioseo-settings-132x60.png 132w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/aioseo-settings-198x90.png 198w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/aioseo-settings.png 1434w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Here are some simple steps to begin your learning journey.</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Learn what a title tag is and <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/seo-title-tags/\">how to optimize it</a>.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Learn what a meta description is and <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-write-meta-descriptions-for-seo/\">how to optimize it</a>.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Learn what alt tags are and how to <a href=\"https://www.wpbeginner.com/beginners-guide/image-alt-text-vs-image-title-in-wordpress-whats-the-difference/\">add them to images</a>.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Learn what a target keyword (<a href=\"https://aioseo.com/docs/using-the-focus-keyphrase-to-analyze-your-content/\">focus keyphrase</a>) is and how to use it.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Learn what <a href=\"https://www.blogtyrant.com/how-to-easily-find-the-best-keywords/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" title=\"\">keyword research</a> is and how it can help your articles rank.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Learn what <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-add-rich-snippets-to-wordpress/\">rich snippets</a> are and how to add them to pages.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"493\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/product-schema-1-1024x493.jpg\" alt=\"rich snippet example\" class=\"wp-image-173009\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/product-schema-1-1024x493.jpg 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/product-schema-1-300x144.jpg 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/product-schema-1-768x370.jpg 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/product-schema-1-600x289.jpg 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/product-schema-1-125x60.jpg 125w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/product-schema-1-187x90.jpg 187w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/product-schema-1.jpg 1070w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\"><em>Learn how to </em><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-add-product-review-schema-in-wordpress/\"><em>add product schema</em></a><em> to get these types of search snippets.</em></figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"aioseo-bonus-seo-tips\">Bonus SEO Tips</h2>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Business directory listings</strong> impact your ranking. And they&#8217;re easy to get. Move forward on this today with our guide <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-get-local-seo-citations/\">How to Get Local SEO Citations</a>.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Reviews can provide valuable <strong>customer feedback</strong>. Learn from the positive and negative Google Reviews.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Google review policies</strong>: Google doesn&#8217;t allow misrepresentation or misinformation in reviews. Fake reviews and paid reviews are also policy violations. Find out more <a href=\"https://support.google.com/local-guides/answer/7400114?hl=en\">here</a>.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Customer experience</strong>: Every business owner wants interactions and sales to result in happy customers. Take time to think through what you want the customer experience to be like: from when they first hear of your brand to when you ask for a review.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Plan for conversions</strong>: Make the most of your SEO efforts by planning calls-to-action (CTAs). WordPress users will like OptinMonster, a beginner-friendly, low-cost tool that&#8217;s effective in<a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/lead-generation/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" title=\"\"> boosting conversions and sales</a>. (We use it too.)</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"aioseo-summing-it-up\">Summing it Up</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Being proactive with Google Reviews is part of your online reputation management.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Good review management, plus business directory listings and website SEO, can elevate your visibility in google searches and influence consumer purchasing decisions.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"aioseo-whats-next\">What’s Next?</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>We hope this post helped you learn why Google Reviews are important and how to manage them for positive impact.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>You can also check out our article <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/what-is-nap-in-seo/\">What is NAP in SEO?</a> and <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/small-business-seo-scams-how-to-detect-and-avoid-them/\" title=\"\">How to Avoid SEO Scams</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you found this article helpful, then please subscribe to our <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/c/AIOSEO\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">YouTube Channel</a>. You’ll find many more helpful tutorials there. You can also follow us on <a href=\"https://twitter.com/aioseopack\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">Twitter</a>, <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/company/aioseo/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">LinkedIn</a>, or <a href=\"https://facebook.com/aioseopack/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">Facebook</a> to stay in the loop.</p>The post <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-manage-google-reviews-for-improved-seo/\">How to Manage Google Reviews for Improved SEO (Small Business Guide)</a> first appeared on <a href=\"https://aioseo.com\">AIOSEO</a>.\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:70:\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-manage-google-reviews-for-improved-seo/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:8;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:85:\"\n		\n		\n					\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n					\n										\n					\n					\n			\n		\n		\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:65:\"How to Write Meta Descriptions for SEO (Boost CTR &amp; Rankings)\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:140:\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-write-meta-descriptions-for-seo/?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=how-to-write-meta-descriptions-for-seo\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:66:\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-write-meta-descriptions-for-seo/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Mon, 27 Mar 2023 14:27:36 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:5:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"Tutorials\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:30:\"how to write meta descriptions\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:38:\"how to write meta descriptions for seo\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:26:\"meta description generator\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:4;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:27:\"meta descriptions wordpress\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:27:\"https://aioseo.com/?p=37991\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:541:\"<p>Do you want to know how to write meta descriptions for SEO that’ll increase your organic search traffic, CTR (Click-Through-Rate), and rankings on Google? In this post, we’ll show you how to write meta descriptions for SEO, and to easily add them in WordPress. We’ll also cover what a meta description is and why you need it.</p>\nThe post <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-write-meta-descriptions-for-seo/\">How to Write Meta Descriptions for SEO (Boost CTR & Rankings)</a> first appeared on <a href=\"https://aioseo.com\">AIOSEO</a>.\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"Kato Nkhoma\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31791:\"<p>Do you want to know how to write meta descriptions for SEO that’ll increase your organic search traffic, CTR (Click-Through-Rate), and rankings on Google?</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Research by <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/ahrefs\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\">Ahrefs</a> has shown that 74.98% of the top 10 ranking web pages have a meta description, which means it’s important to optimize yours for SEO.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>In this article, we’ll show you how to easily write meta descriptions for SEO and add them in WordPress. We’ll also cover what a meta description is and why you need it.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Here’s a quick overview of what we’ll cover in this post. Simply click on these quick links to jump straight to different sections:</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"is-layout-flow wp-block-group aioseo-table-of-contents has-theme-info-background-color has-background\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>In This Article</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-aioseo-table-of-contents\"><ul><li><a href=\"#what-is-a-meta-description-in-wordpress\">What Is a Meta Description in WordPress?</a></li><li><a href=\"#why-do-you-need-a-meta-description\">Why Do You Need a Meta Description?</a></li><li><a href=\"#how-to-write-meta-descriptions-for-seo\">How to Write Meta Descriptions for SEO?</a><ul><li><a href=\"#aioseo-1-include-your-focus-keyword\">1. Include Your Focus Keyword</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-2-describe-your-pages-content\">2. Describe Your Page’s Content</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-3-include-a-call-to-action-to-increase-ctr\">3. Include a Call to Action to Increase CTR</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-4-be-unique-and-interesting\">4. Be Unique and Interesting</a></li></ul></li><li><a href=\"#easily-add-your-meta-description-in-wordpress\">Easily Add Your Meta Descriptions in WordPress</a><ul><li><a href=\"#aioseo-use-the-ai-title-description-generator-to-effortlessly-create-meta-descriptions-with-1-click\">How to Automatically Add Meta Descriptions Using the AI Title/Description Generator (1-Click)</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-adding-your-meta-description\">How to Manually Add Your Meta Description</a><ul></ul></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-easily-double-check-that-youve-added-your-focus-keyword\">Easily Double-Check That You&#8217;ve Added Your Focus Keyword</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-analyzing-your-seo\">Analyzing Your SEO</a></li></ul></li></ul></div>\n</div></div>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li></li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Alright, let’s get started by first explaining what a meta description in WordPress is.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"what-is-a-meta-description-in-wordpress\">What Is a Meta Description in WordPress?</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>A meta description in WordPress is an HTML element or attribute that gives a brief summary of what your web page is about.&nbsp;It gives searchers a sneak peek of your article on <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/what-are-serps/\" title=\"What Are SERPs (And Why Are they Important to SEO)?\">search engine results pages</a> (SERPs), hopefully encouraging them to click on your search listing.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Here’s an example of a meta description on Google for the search query: “best keto recipes”:</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"730\" height=\"173\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/example-of-meta-description-on-google.png\" alt=\"Example of a meta description in Google\'s search results\" class=\"wp-image-33479\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/example-of-meta-description-on-google.png 730w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/example-of-meta-description-on-google-300x71.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/example-of-meta-description-on-google-600x142.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 730px) 100vw, 730px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Google and other search engines often show the meta description in their search results. So by writing good, interesting and actionable meta descriptions, you can get more people to click through to your website and increase sales for your business.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"why-do-you-need-a-meta-description\">Why Do You Need a Meta Description?</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Meta descriptions won’t directly help you rank, but compelling and actionable meta descriptions will convince more people to click on those links. More clicks mean more traffic, and it can also lead to higher rankings in search engines.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Additionally, meta descriptions let Google know what your page is about. Even though Google doesn’t always use your meta description and sometimes adds its own based on your content, you should write them in case it does. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Writing good meta descriptions is especially important for your homepage, product and category pages since they help in establishing your brand.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"how-to-write-meta-descriptions-for-seo\">How to Write Meta Descriptions for SEO?</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>When it comes to writing meta descriptions for SEO, you should do the following:</p>\n\n\n\n<ol>\n<li>Include Your Focus Keyword&nbsp;</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Describe Your Page’s Content&nbsp;</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Include a Call to Action </li>\n\n\n\n<li>Make Them Unique and Interesting</li>\n</ol>\n\n\n\n<p>We understand that this can feel like a lot&#8230;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>&#8230;but depending on the niche you’re active in and the purpose of your site, you should at least try to implement as many of the above as possible to maximize your search traffic, clicks, and rankings. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Let’s dig in a bit deeper&#8230;</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-1-include-your-focus-keyword\">1. Include Your Focus Keyword</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Every meta description should include the focus keyword or keyphrase that you want to rank for.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Always start by <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/best-seo-keyword-analysis-tool/\" title=\"8 Best SEO Keyword Analysis Tools You Need to Know in 2023\">performing keyword research</a> to find the best keywords for your content that have search volume and will match the search intent.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Adding your focus keyword is also important because Google highlights search terms by bolding them when they match the user’s search terms. This helps users to notice them more easily.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>For example, here you can see how Google has highlighted the search terms from the search query: “best SEO plugin for WordPress”:</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"702\" height=\"213\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/how-to-write-meta-descriptions-example.png\" alt=\"Example of how to write meta descriptions and including the keyword.\" class=\"wp-image-172152\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/how-to-write-meta-descriptions-example.png 702w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/how-to-write-meta-descriptions-example-300x91.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/how-to-write-meta-descriptions-example-600x182.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/how-to-write-meta-descriptions-example-190x58.png 190w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/how-to-write-meta-descriptions-example-297x90.png 297w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 702px) 100vw, 702px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>As you can see, it only takes a second to scan this meta description to see that it answers the search query, resulting in more clicks and higher rankings.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-2-describe-your-pages-content\">2. Describe Your Page’s Content</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>A good meta description should describe your page’s content. The recommended character limit is 155-160 characters, so you need to summarize your most important content in about 2 sentences.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>AIOSEO will help you get the right length. It shows how many characters you&#8217;ve used and warns if you exceed the max recommended characters for your meta description. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"730\" height=\"173\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/max-recommended-characters-meta-description-in-asioseo.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-38156\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/max-recommended-characters-meta-description-in-asioseo.png 730w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/max-recommended-characters-meta-description-in-asioseo-300x71.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/max-recommended-characters-meta-description-in-asioseo-600x142.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/max-recommended-characters-meta-description-in-asioseo-190x45.png 190w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/max-recommended-characters-meta-description-in-asioseo-380x90.png 380w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 730px) 100vw, 730px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>As easy as 1-2-3!</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-3-include-a-call-to-action-to-increase-ctr\">3. Include a Call to Action to Increase CTR</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>A call to action can prompt searchers not only to click on your link but also to do something once they arrive on your site. For example, <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/best-business-voip-and-internet-phone-systems/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">call a phone number</a>, sign up for a free trial, or take a special action.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Here’s an example of MonsterInsights meta description, which lets people know that they can <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-set-up-google-analytics-on-a-wordpress-site/\" title=\"How to Set Up Google Analytics on a WordPress Site (Easy Way)\">set up Google Analytics for WordPress</a> with just a few clicks:&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"730\" height=\"147\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/call-to-action-meta-description-1.png\" alt=\"Call to action meta description for the best analytics plugin for WordPress MonsterInsights\" class=\"wp-image-38158\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/call-to-action-meta-description-1.png 730w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/call-to-action-meta-description-1-300x60.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/call-to-action-meta-description-1-600x121.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/call-to-action-meta-description-1-190x38.png 190w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/call-to-action-meta-description-1-447x90.png 447w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 730px) 100vw, 730px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>In addition, the stats of 12 million downloads will also work as proof that other website owners are using the plugin and encourage searchers to download it as well. </p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-4-be-unique-and-interesting\">4. Be Unique and Interesting</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Many large sites auto-populate their meta descriptions, so the first thing you should do is to make sure they’re unique and interesting.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Ask yourself this question: Would the meta description spike your interest to want to know more and click on the link? Put yourself in your customer’s shoes.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Does this sound overwhelming?</p>\n\n\n\n<p>No need to worry because AIOSEO helps you easily write meta descriptions for SEO and add them to your site in a heartbeat, which we’ll show you next.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"easily-add-your-meta-description-in-wordpress\">Easily Add Your Meta Descriptions in WordPress</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>One of the easiest ways to add meta descriptions in WordPress is to use a powerful SEO plugin like <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/pricing/\" title=\"Pricing\">All In One SEO</a> (AIOSEO).</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><a href=\"https://aioseo.com\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"730\" height=\"44