ion generator, <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-use-a-meta-description-generator-in-wordpress/\" title=\"How to Use a Meta Description Generator in WordPress\">check out this guide</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-adding-your-meta-description\">How to Manually Add Your Meta Description</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>To manually add meta descriptions to your articles, simply scroll down in the post or page you’re editing to the <strong>AIOSEO Settings</strong>.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"702\" height=\"282\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/how-to-write-meta-descriptions-for-seo-settings.png\" alt=\"Snippet preview in the AIOSEO settings\" class=\"wp-image-170337\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/how-to-write-meta-descriptions-for-seo-settings.png 702w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/how-to-write-meta-descriptions-for-seo-settings-300x121.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/how-to-write-meta-descriptions-for-seo-settings-600x241.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/how-to-write-meta-descriptions-for-seo-settings-149x60.png 149w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/how-to-write-meta-descriptions-for-seo-settings-224x90.png 224w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 702px) 100vw, 702px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Here you’ll first see a <strong>Snippet</strong> <strong>Preview</strong> that shows an example of how your content will look in search results based on the Title and Meta Description you enter.</p>\n\n\n\n<h4 id=\"aioseo-using-smart-tags-in-your-meta-description\">Using Smart Tags in Your Meta Description</h4>\n\n\n\n<p>And to make it super easy for you to optimize your meta descriptions in WordPress, AIOSEO has added pre-installed smart tags with different variables you can use.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>To start adding them, you need to scroll down to the <strong>Meta Description </strong>section and then click on any of the smart tags. In this example, we’ve added the <strong>+ Post Excerpt </strong>smart tag.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"702\" height=\"211\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/how-to-write-meta-descriptions-for-seo-post-excerpt.png\" alt=\"Adding your meta description using smart tags in All in One SEO\" class=\"wp-image-170344\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/how-to-write-meta-descriptions-for-seo-post-excerpt.png 702w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/how-to-write-meta-descriptions-for-seo-post-excerpt-300x90.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/how-to-write-meta-descriptions-for-seo-post-excerpt-600x180.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/how-to-write-meta-descriptions-for-seo-post-excerpt-190x57.png 190w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/how-to-write-meta-descriptions-for-seo-post-excerpt-299x90.png 299w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 702px) 100vw, 702px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>AIOSEO will then automatically add your post&#8217;s excerpt as meta description.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>And you can also include other variables, such as <strong>+ Author First Name</strong> or<strong> </strong>+<strong> Author Last Name</strong>.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"702\" height=\"385\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/how-to-write-meta-descriptions-for-seo-smart-tags.png\" alt=\"View all smart tags in All in One SEO\" class=\"wp-image-170349\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/how-to-write-meta-descriptions-for-seo-smart-tags.png 702w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/how-to-write-meta-descriptions-for-seo-smart-tags-300x165.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/how-to-write-meta-descriptions-for-seo-smart-tags-600x329.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/how-to-write-meta-descriptions-for-seo-smart-tags-109x60.png 109w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/how-to-write-meta-descriptions-for-seo-smart-tags-164x90.png 164w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 702px) 100vw, 702px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>To see all of the smart tags, click on the <strong>View all tags</strong> link.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<h4 id=\"aioseo-manually-entering-your-meta-description\">Manually Entering Your Meta Description in WordPress</h4>\n\n\n\n<p>You also have the option to enter your meta description manually. Simply type in your description directly into the field.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"702\" height=\"234\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/how-to-write-meta-descriptions-for-seo-manual.png\" alt=\"Type in your meta description in the provided field.\" class=\"wp-image-170352\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/how-to-write-meta-descriptions-for-seo-manual.png 702w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/how-to-write-meta-descriptions-for-seo-manual-300x100.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/how-to-write-meta-descriptions-for-seo-manual-600x200.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/how-to-write-meta-descriptions-for-seo-manual-180x60.png 180w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/how-to-write-meta-descriptions-for-seo-manual-270x90.png 270w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 702px) 100vw, 702px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Don’t forget that the meta description should also include your focus keyword or keyphrase.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Plus, with AIOSEO, you can also <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-add-emojis-to-your-seo-titles-and-meta-descriptions/\" title=\"How to Add Emojis to Your SEO Titles and Meta Descriptions\">add emojis to your meta descriptions</a>. Doing so makes them stand out on SERPs, resulting in a <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/ways-to-increase-your-organic-clickthrough-rates/\" title=\"8 Proven Ways to Increase Your Organic Clickthrough Rates\">boost in clicks</a> and SEO.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-easily-double-check-that-youve-added-your-focus-keyword\">Easily Double-Check That You&#8217;ve Added Your Focus Keyword</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>With AIOSEO, you even get an analysis of your focus keyword or keyphrase. It&#8217;ll check that you’ve used it in the meta description and other areas that&#8217;ll help to improve your SEO.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"730\" height=\"350\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/focus-keyphrase-analysis-in-all-in-one-seo.png\" alt=\"Analyzing the focus keyphrase in meta description in All in One SEO\" class=\"wp-image-37999\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/focus-keyphrase-analysis-in-all-in-one-seo.png 730w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/focus-keyphrase-analysis-in-all-in-one-seo-300x144.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/focus-keyphrase-analysis-in-all-in-one-seo-600x288.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/focus-keyphrase-analysis-in-all-in-one-seo-125x60.png 125w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/focus-keyphrase-analysis-in-all-in-one-seo-188x90.png 188w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 730px) 100vw, 730px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>This helps ensure that your meta descriptions are SEO-friendly.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-analyzing-your-seo\">Analyzing Your SEO</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>AIOSEO makes it easy to improve your SEO with its SEO analysis tool.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>In the <strong>Basic SEO</strong> section, you can view an SEO analysis of your whole page&#8217;s content and get tons of helpful tips to boost your overall SEO score.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"730\" height=\"369\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/aioseo-page-analysis-basic-seo-1.png\" alt=\"Basic SEO analysis in All in One SEO\" class=\"wp-image-37351\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/aioseo-page-analysis-basic-seo-1.png 730w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/aioseo-page-analysis-basic-seo-1-300x152.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/aioseo-page-analysis-basic-seo-1-600x303.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/aioseo-page-analysis-basic-seo-1-119x60.png 119w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/aioseo-page-analysis-basic-seo-1-178x90.png 178w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 730px) 100vw, 730px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>It tells you what you’ve optimized well and gives recommendations on what you need to improve (which will be marked in red).</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The <strong>Page Analysis</strong> even analyzes your <strong>Title</strong> and gives immediate results on the title length, if the title has a number, and includes <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/700-power-words-that-will-boost-your-conversions/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">power words or sentiment words</a>. These are important factors to attract more clicks.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"730\" height=\"241\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/title-analysis-in-all-in-one-seo-1.png\" alt=\"SEO title analysis in All in One SEO\" class=\"wp-image-33477\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/title-analysis-in-all-in-one-seo-1.png 730w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/title-analysis-in-all-in-one-seo-1-300x99.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/title-analysis-in-all-in-one-seo-1-600x198.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 730px) 100vw, 730px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The<strong> Readability</strong> tool is also useful since Google has increased its focus on how well your content reads and is structured.&nbsp;The longer you get users to stay on your page, the more useful Google thinks your content is and will favor it.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"730\" height=\"551\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/aioseo-page-analysis-readability.png\" alt=\"Readability analysis in All in One SEO\" class=\"wp-image-37353\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/aioseo-page-analysis-readability.png 730w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/aioseo-page-analysis-readability-300x226.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/aioseo-page-analysis-readability-600x453.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/aioseo-page-analysis-readability-79x60.png 79w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/aioseo-page-analysis-readability-119x90.png 119w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 730px) 100vw, 730px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>As you can see, the Readability analysis gives you lots of valuable tips on how to improve your content and boost your rankings on Google.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>In addition, if you also want to learn how to optimize your SEO title, you can check out <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-change-the-seo-title-in-wordpress/\" title=\"How to Easily Change the SEO Title in WordPress (Step by Step)\">how to change your SEO title in WordPress</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>And there you have it!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Use these tips to start crafting compelling and actionable meta descriptions and watch your search traffic, click-through rate, and rankings improve quickly.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>We hope this post helped you learn how to write meta descriptions for SEO and easily add them to your WordPress site using AIOSEO. You may also want to check out other articles on our blog, like our <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/ultimate-wordpress-seo-guide/\" title=\"Ultimate WordPress SEO Guide: Optimize Your Site in 2023\">ultimate WordPress SEO guide</a> or our list of <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/seo-best-practices/\" title=\"SEO Best Practices: 20 Ultimate SEO Tips to Boost Rankings\">SEO best practices</a> to help you rank higher on search engines.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you found this article helpful, then please subscribe to our <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/c/AIOSEO\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">YouTube Channel</a>. You’ll find many more helpful tutorials there. You can also follow us on <a href=\"https://twitter.com/aioseopack\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">Twitter</a>, <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/company/aioseo/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">LinkedIn</a>, or <a href=\"https://facebook.com/aioseopack/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">Facebook</a> to stay in the loop.</p>The post <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-write-meta-descriptions-for-seo/\">How to Write Meta Descriptions for SEO (Boost CTR & Rankings)</a> first appeared on <a href=\"https://aioseo.com\">AIOSEO</a>.\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:63:\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-write-meta-descriptions-for-seo/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:9;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:88:\"\n		\n		\n					\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n					\n										\n					\n					\n			\n		\n		\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:55:\"How to Use a Google Business Profile to Boost Local SEO\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:178:\"https://aioseo.com/ho