 87% of consumers use Google to evaluate local businesses. Creating a Google Business Profile is part of giving your small business every advantage. In this article, you&#8217;ll&#8230;</p>\nThe post <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-use-a-google-business-profile-to-imrpove-local-seo/\">How to Use a Google Business Profile to Boost Local SEO</a> first appeared on <a href=\"https://aioseo.com\">AIOSEO</a>.\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:15:\"Sherrie Gossett\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31845:\"<p>Wondering whether setting up a Google Business Profile is worth your time?</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Around <a href=\"https://www.brightlocal.com/research/local-consumer-review-survey/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">87%</a> of consumers use Google to evaluate local businesses. Creating a Google Business Profile is part of giving your small business every advantage.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>In this article, you&#8217;ll find out how a Google Business Profile benefits business owners, how to set one up today, and how to optimize it for SEO.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"is-layout-flow wp-block-group aioseo-table-of-contents has-theme-info-background-color has-background\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>In This Article</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-aioseo-table-of-contents\"><ul><li><a href=\"#aioseo-what-is-a-google-business-profile\">What&#8217;s a Google Business Profile?</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-benefits-of-google-my-business-profile-gbp\">Benefits</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-how-to-create-a-google-my-business-profile\">How to Create Your Profile</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-how-to-optimize-your-google-business-profile-for-seo\">How to Optimize it</a><ul></ul></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-importance-of-star-ratings-and-reviews\">How to Manage Your Reviews for SEO</a><ul></ul></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-next-optimize-your-website\">Next: Optimize Your Website</a><ul></ul></li></ul></div>\n</div></div>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"aioseo-what-is-a-google-business-profile\">What is a Google Business Profile?</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Google Business Profile is a free tool you can use to display your business information, hours, and contact information across local search results.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>It&#8217;s easy to set up: you&#8217;ll create an account and fill in your information.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Once complete, your business will have a prominent display that appears in local search results including in Google Maps searches.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Here&#8217;s an example of a Google Business Profile appearing in a search for &#8220;Brasserie Blanc Leeds.&#8221;</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"588\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-business-profile-example-1-1024x588.jpg\" alt=\"google business profile brasserie blanc\" class=\"wp-image-170749\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-business-profile-example-1-1024x588.jpg 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-business-profile-example-1-300x172.jpg 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-business-profile-example-1-768x441.jpg 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-business-profile-example-1-600x344.jpg 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-business-profile-example-1-105x60.jpg 105w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-business-profile-example-1-157x90.jpg 157w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-business-profile-example-1.jpg 1371w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>If you do the same search in <strong>Google Maps</strong>, on a desktop, the profile displays to the left of the map.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"636\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-business-profile-google-maps-1024x636.jpg\" alt=\"google business profile in google maps\" class=\"wp-image-170751\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-business-profile-google-maps-1024x636.jpg 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-business-profile-google-maps-300x186.jpg 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-business-profile-google-maps-768x477.jpg 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-business-profile-google-maps-1536x954.jpg 1536w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-business-profile-google-maps-2048x1272.jpg 2048w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-business-profile-google-maps-600x373.jpg 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-business-profile-google-maps-97x60.jpg 97w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-business-profile-google-maps-145x90.jpg 145w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The profile provides searchers with useful information like the hours the restaurant is open, and whether they offer dining-in or strictly take-out.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Searchers can even book a table without leaving Google Maps.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-aioseo-theme-notice-box\" role=\"alert\">\n<p>Google Business Profile was formerly called Google My Business (or GMB for short). </p>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"aioseo-benefits-of-google-my-business-profile-gbp\">Benefits of Google My Business Profile (GBP)</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Because these profiles are prominent in search results, they offer several benefits.</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Your profile information appears in several different areas of local search, including Google Maps.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Google Star ratings and reviews of your business will be visible in your profile.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>You can create a strong first impression with the profile.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Used well, your profile can boost <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/lead-generation/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" title=\"\">conversions</a> too.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Additionally, Google Business Profile is perceived to be the single most important local SEO ranking factor, according to a recent <a href=\"https://whitespark.ca/local-search-ranking-factors/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">survey</a> of marketing professionals.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"aioseo-how-to-create-a-google-my-business-profile\">How to Create a Google My Business Profile</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>To create a Google My Business Profile go to google.com/business.</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Click the <strong>Manage Now</strong> button to get started.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>You&#8217;ll be given an option to login with an existing Gmail address or to create a new Google account or new Gmail address.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>From there, follow Google&#8217;s prompts.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>The instructions are clear and easy to follow.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>You&#8217;ll add location (if applicable) and contact information. It&#8217;s not mandatory to list a location. Businesses without a storefront or physical location can simply skip the location step.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>You can also add photos and videos along with news, announcements, or offers.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"aioseo-how-to-optimize-your-google-business-profile-for-seo\">How to Optimize Your Google Business Profile for SEO</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Optimizing your profile for SEO is simple. Some of these recommended steps are one-time actions. Others are ongoing. Let&#8217;s dive in.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-business-category-be-precise\">Business Category: Be Precise</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>It pays to be <strong><em>precise</em></strong> about the business categories you select: These will impact what searches your business appears in. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>(You&#8217;ll select a primary category for your business. You also have the option to select secondary categories.)</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"890\" height=\"719\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-business-profile-categories.png\" alt=\"google business profile categories\" class=\"wp-image-170752\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-business-profile-categories.png 890w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-business-profile-categories-300x242.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-business-profile-categories-768x620.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-business-profile-categories-600x485.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-business-profile-categories-74x60.png 74w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-business-profile-categories-111x90.png 111w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Don’t be surprised if Google updates your category. It may do so if you’ve chosen the wrong one. In this case, when you log in, you’ll see a message asking you to accept Google’s revision.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-completeness-more-is-better\">Completeness: More is Better</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Take care to make your profile as complete as possible. This will include filling in all relevant information.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>And take advantage of the option to post inviting photos or offers. Your Google Business Profile is a prominent part of local search, and you can control how your business appears.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-keep-business-hours-updated\">Keep Business Hours Updated</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Google strives to offer the most reliable, as well as relevant, information to local searchers.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>For this reason it&#8217;s important to ensure that your hours are updated for holidays or are changed when necessary.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Remember: <em>Your hours will also show up in Google Maps searches</em>. The last thing any small business wants is someone complaining on Google that they drove to a business that was listed as open, but it was closed.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-keep-your-nap-up-to-date-and-consistent\">Keep Your NAP Up-to-Date and Consistent</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>The same holds true for &#8220;NAP&#8221; — your business Name, Address, and Phone number. When these change, immediately update your Google Business Profile.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>You&#8217;ll also want to update your NAP on other sites, like your social media profiles, your website, and any listings in business directories. To update the latter, follow our <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-get-local-seo-citations/\">simple instructions here</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Keeping your <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/what-is-nap-in-seo/\">NAP consistent</a> across the internet is important for SEO.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-take-advantage-of-google-business-profiles-special-features\">Take Advantage of Google Business Profile&#8217;s Special Features</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>There are a number of special features available in Google Business Profile that can help you attract new customers.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>For example,</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Service-based businesses can include a link to <strong>book appointments.</strong></li>\n\n\n\n<li>Ecommerce stores can list <strong>products</strong> along with prices and stock status.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Restaurants can post their menu, provide buttons for &#8220;<strong>Order takeout</strong>&#8221; or &#8220;<strong>Order delivery</strong>.&#8221;</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full is-resized\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-business-profile-restaurant.png\" alt=\"google business profile restaurant\" class=\"wp-image-170747\" width=\"500\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-business-profile-restaurant.png 838w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-business-profile-restaurant-285x300.png 285w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-business-profile-restaurant-768x809.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-business-profile-restaurant-600x632.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-business-profile-restaurant-57x60.png 57w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-business-profile-restaurant-85x90.png 85w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-keep-your-profile-updated\">Keep Your Profile Updated</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>The most common mistake we see small business owners making with Google Business Profile is they set it up, then ignore it.</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Adding new content to your profile conveys to searchers, and Google, that your business is active and thriving.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Special offers posted to your profile can attract new customers.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Replies to Google reviews can sway customers as well.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Indeed, recency of reviews is a factor that can impact your rankings and persuade searchers to choose your business.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>It&#8217;s worth taking a close look at how <strong>star ratings</strong> and <strong>reviews work</strong>, and what you need to do to optimize them for SEO.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"aioseo-importance-of-star-ratings-and-reviews\">Importance of Star Ratings and Reviews</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>All Google Business Profiles feature a star rating for that business. This star rating is the average of all customer ratings. The total number of customer reviews displays next to it.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>These star ratings and reviews have a big impact on buyer decisions.</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.brightlocal.com/research/local-consumer-review-survey/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">98%</a> of searchers read online reviews of local businesses</li>\n\n\n\n<li>And Google is &#8220;the most trusted review platform,&#8221; according to BrightLocal research.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Interestingly, star ratings show up in several areas of Google Search.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>They show up in the Local Pack.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"551\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-star-ratings-local-pack-1024x551.jpg\" alt=\"google star ratings in search results\" class=\"wp-image-170754\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-star-ratings-local-pack-1024x551.jpg 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-star-ratings-local-pack-300x161.jpg 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-star-ratings-local-pack-768x413.jpg 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-star-ratings-local-pack-1536x827.jpg 1536w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-star-ratings-local-pack-2048x1102.jpg 2048w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-star-ratings-local-pack-600x323.jpg 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-star-ratings-local-pack-111x60.jpg 111w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-star-ratings-local-pack-167x90.jpg 167w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>They appear in Google Maps searches when users click or mouseover a pin.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"491\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/star-ratings-google-maps-1024x491.jpg\" alt=\"star ratings in google maps\" class=\"wp-image-170755\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/star-ratings-google-maps-1024x491.jpg 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/star-ratings-google-maps-300x144.jpg 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/star-ratings-google-maps-768x369.jpg 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/star-ratings-google-maps-1536x737.jpg 1536w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/star-ratings-google-maps-600x288.jpg 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/star-ratings-google-maps-125x60.jpg 125w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/star-ratings-google-maps-188x90.jpg 188w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/star-ratings-google-maps.jpg 1596w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>And they appear in Google Ads, including <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/what-are-local-services-ads/\">Local Services Ads</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"359\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/local-services-ads-star-ratings-1024x359.png\" alt=\"examples of google local services ads\" class=\"wp-image-170757\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/local-services-ads-star-ratings-1024x359.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/local-services-ads-star-ratings-300x105.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/local-services-ads-star-ratings-768x269.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/local-services-ads-star-ratings-1536x538.png 1536w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/local-services-ads-star-ratings-2048x718.png 2048w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/local-services-ads-star-ratings-600x210.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/local-services-ads-star-ratings-171x60.png 171w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/local-services-ads-star-ratings-257x90.png 257w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>So, consumers are seeing these star ratings for your local business <em>everywhere.</em></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Here&#8217;s how you can make the most of this.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-continue-soliciting-reviews\">Continue Soliciting Reviews</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>After you get your first 5 or 10 reviews, don&#8217;t stop. Make it a habit to ask for reviews from every customer.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Research shows that around <a href=\"https://www.brightlocal.com/research/local-consumer-review-survey-2022/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">73%</a> of local shoppers are swayed by the presence of <em>recent </em>reviews of a business.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>And a Semrush <a href=\"https://www.semrush.com/blog/local-seo-rankings/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">study</a> suggests that <em>quantity</em> of reviews is more important than the star rating average, <em>as long as the average is 4.1 or higher</em>.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-aim-to-increase-your-star-rating-average\">Aim to Increase Your Star Rating Average</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>While quantity may be more important quality, the Semrush study, like all research of its type, relies on averages. What works best for your business may fall outside of those averages.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Besides, a higher star rating average may help your business increase trust, traffic, and revenue.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>To give yourself every advantage, set a goal to increase your star rating average.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>We do this ourselves. Many businesses have found this practice to be useful.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Not surprisingly, the BrightLocal study we cited above showed that:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><strong>85%</strong> of searchers consider the overall average star rating of a business to be “important” of “very important.”</li>\n\n\n\n<li>When <em>comparing</em> businesses, <strong>76% </strong>of searchers considered which one had the higher average star rating.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-respond-promptly\">Respond Promptly</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Create a routine for responding promptly to reviews. This shows that your business&#8217;s customer service is active.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>And respond proactively to negative reviews. Consider creating a templated routine that staff can use when responding: that may include text and actions.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Remember: People can later change and update their reviews. More importantly, others will get a positive impression of your customer service.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Don’t be too concerned about negative reviews. Google <a href=\"https://support.google.com/business/answer/3474122?hl=en\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">reports</a> that &#8220;Customers find a mix of positive and negative reviews <em>more trustworthy</em>.&#8221;</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"aioseo-next-optimize-your-website\">Next: Optimize Your Website</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>While Google Business Profile and <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-manage-google-reviews-for-improved-seo/\" title=\"\">customer reviews</a> are key factors for local ranking, they’re not the only ones. How well your <em>website</em> ranks also impacts how your business performs in the Local Pack.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>As Google puts it: “Your position in web results is also a factor, so search engine optimization (SEO) best practices apply.”</p>\n\n\n\n<p>This is where a plugin like <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/pricing/\">All in One SEO (AIOSEO)</a> comes in.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Designed to enable beginners to get pro-level results, this plugin makes complicated SEO tasks as simple as clicking buttons and filling out forms.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"485\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/aioseo-homepage-1024x485.png\" alt=\"aioseo homepage\" class=\"wp-image-140989\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/aioseo-homepage-1024x485.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/aioseo-homepage-300x142.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/aioseo-homepage-768x364.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/aioseo-homepage-600x284.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/aioseo-homepage-127x60.png 127w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/aioseo-homepage-190x90.png 190w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/aioseo-homepage.png 1260w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>All in One SEO (AIOSEO) has thousands of 5-star ratings on WordPress.org. And it&#8217;s currently used by over 3 million sites.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>As an added bonus, you’ll get access to AIOSEO’s world-class support team, staffed with experienced software engineers.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-set-up-local-seo-basics\">Step 1: Set Up Local SEO Basics</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Once you&#8217;ve <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/pricing/\">downloaded</a> and <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/docs/installing-all-in-one-seo-pro/\">installed the plugin</a>, you’re ready to set up your local SEO basics.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>In the WordPress admin bar go to <strong>AIOSEO » Local SEO</strong>.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"454\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/aioseo-local-seo-menu-1024x454.jpg\" alt=\"aioseo local seo\" class=\"wp-image-154766\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/aioseo-local-seo-menu-1024x454.jpg 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/aioseo-local-seo-menu-300x133.jpg 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/aioseo-local-seo-menu-768x340.jpg 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/aioseo-local-seo-menu-1536x680.jpg 1536w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/aioseo-local-seo-menu-2048x907.jpg 2048w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/aioseo-local-seo-menu-600x266.jpg 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/aioseo-local-seo-menu-135x60.jpg 135w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/aioseo-local-seo-menu-203x90.jpg 203w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\"><em>The admin bar is the black horizontal bar at the top of the WordPress editor. Hovering your cursor over the AIOSEO logo will cause a drop-down list of menu items to appear.</em></figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>That will open a window with 3 tabs: for <strong>Locations</strong>, <strong>Opening Hours</strong>, and <strong>Maps</strong>.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"478\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/aioseo-local-seo-settings-1024x478.png\" alt=\"aioseo local seo settings\" class=\"wp-image-154770\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/aioseo-local-seo-settings-1024x478.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/aioseo-local-seo-settings-300x140.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/aioseo-local-seo-settings-768x359.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/aioseo-local-seo-settings-600x280.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/aioseo-local-seo-settings-128x60.png 128w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/aioseo-local-seo-settings-193x90.png 193w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/aioseo-local-seo-settings.png 1353w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Click on each tab.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Then fill in the requested information.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>This local SEO process adds code called <em>schema markup</em> to your website. The code helps Google understand your content better and match your business to relevant search queries.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-step-2-check-your-seo-analysis\">Step 2: Check Your Homepage SEO</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Next, review your homepage for improvements.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>To do this, in the WordPress admin bar, navigate to <strong>AIOSEO » SEO Analysis.</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"517\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/aioseo-seo-analysis-1024x517.png\" alt=\"aioseo seo analysis menu item\" class=\"wp-image-170734\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/aioseo-seo-analysis-1024x517.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/aioseo-seo-analysis-300x151.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/aioseo-seo-analysis-768x388.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/aioseo-seo-analysis-1536x776.png 1536w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/aioseo-seo-analysis-2048x1034.png 2048w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/aioseo-seo-analysis-600x303.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/aioseo-seo-analysis-119x60.png 119w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/aioseo-seo-analysis-178x90.png 178w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Now, you&#8217;ll see your website&#8217;s overall <strong>Site Score</strong>.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"520\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/aioseo-site-score-1024x520.png\" alt=\"aioseo site score\" class=\"wp-image-170735\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/aioseo-site-score-1024x520.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/aioseo-site-score-300x152.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/aioseo-site-score-768x390.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/aioseo-site-score-1536x780.png 1536w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/aioseo-site-score-2048x1040.png 2048w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/aioseo-site-score-600x305.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/aioseo-site-score-118x60.png 118w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/aioseo-site-score-177x90.png 177w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>And beneath that is a <strong>Complete SEO Checklist</strong>.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"643\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/aioseo-complete-seo-checklist-1024x643.png\" alt=\"aioseo complete seo checklist\" class=\"wp-image-170737\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/aioseo-complete-seo-checklist-1024x643.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/aioseo-complete-seo-checklist-300x188.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/aioseo-complete-seo-checklist-768x482.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/aioseo-complete-seo-checklist-1536x964.png 1536w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/aioseo-complete-seo-checklist-2048x1286.png 2048w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/aioseo-complete-seo-checklist-600x377.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/aioseo-complete-seo-checklist-96x60.png 96w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/aioseo-complete-seo-checklist-143x90.png 143w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>This checklist provides an analysis of your <strong>homepage </strong>with recommended action items. These are sorted by:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Important Issues (flagged in red)</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Recommended Improvements</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Good results.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>We recommend tackling <strong>Important Issues</strong> first.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Clicking on an item will provide the specific action steps to take.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>For example, this checklist item tells us that our homepage is missing a meta description. And it provides a button to click that will take you to the area you need to add the description to.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"605\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/aioseo-meta-description-missing-1-1024x605.png\" alt=\"aioseo edit meta description\" class=\"wp-image-170739\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/aioseo-meta-description-missing-1-1024x605.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/aioseo-meta-description-missing-1-300x177.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/aioseo-meta-description-missing-1-768x454.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/aioseo-meta-description-missing-1-1536x908.png 1536w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/aioseo-meta-description-missing-1-2048x1211.png 2048w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/aioseo-meta-description-missing-1-600x355.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/aioseo-meta-description-missing-1-101x60.png 101w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/aioseo-meta-description-missing-1-152x90.png 152w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-learn-to-optimize-your-content\">Step 3: Learn to Optimize Your Content</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>When you finish working through the items in your SEO Analysis report, we recommend learning how to optimize individual web pages for SEO.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>You’ll be surprised at how easy it is to learn this. To get started, explore these options:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Learn how to optimize <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/seo-title-tags/\">titles</a> and <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-write-meta-descriptions-for-seo/\">article descriptions</a></li>\n\n\n\n<li>Learn what a <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/docs/using-the-focus-keyphrase-to-analyze-your-content/\">focus keyword</a> is and how to use it.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Learn what <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-add-rich-snippets-to-wordpress/\">rich snippets</a> are and how to create them.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>And bookmark this blog to learn more.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"477\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/product-schema-1024x477.jpg\" alt=\"product schema rich snippet example\" class=\"wp-image-170741\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/product-schema-1024x477.jpg 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/product-schema-300x140.jpg 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/product-schema-768x358.jpg 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/product-schema-600x280.jpg 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/product-schema-129x60.jpg 129w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/product-schema-193x90.jpg 193w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/product-schema.jpg 1180w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\"><em>Above: These search results are rich snippets, made possible with <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-add-product-review-schema-in-wordpress/\" title=\"\">product schema</a> markup</em>.</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"aioseo-whats-next\">What’s Next?</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>We hope this post helped you learn why having a Google Business Profile is important for your small business success and how you can make the most of it.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Also consider exploring <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/what-are-local-services-ads/\">Local Services Ads</a> and how to <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-use-a-wordpress-faq-block-to-boost-seo-and-get-more-traffic/\">get more traffic with FAQs</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you found this article helpful, then please subscribe to our <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/c/AIOSEO\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">YouTube Channel</a>. You’ll find many more helpful tutorials there. You can also follow us on <a href=\"https://twitter.com/aioseopack\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">Twitter</a>, <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/company/aioseo/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">LinkedIn</a>, or <a href=\"https://facebook.com/aioseopack/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">Facebook</a> to stay in the loop.</p>The post <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-use-a-google-business-profile-to-imrpove-local-seo/\">How to Use a Google Business Profile to Boost Local SEO</a> first appeared on <a href=\"https://aioseo.com\">AIOSEO</a>.\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:82:\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-use-a-google-business-profile-to-imrpove-local-seo/feed/\";s:7:\"attrib